(1, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pastawithpurplesprou_3417\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/pastawithpurplesprou_3417_16x9.jpg\n', 'Pasta with purple sprouting broccoli\n', ' Purple sprouting broccoli can be a cheap and cheerful ingredient for early spring dinners and goes brilliantly with anchovy and chilli.\n', 30, 30, 4, 11),
(2, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/ras-el-hanout_chicken_68989\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/ras-el-hanout_chicken_68989_16x9.jpg\n', 'Ras-el-hanout chicken wraps with a yoghurt sauce\n', ' Looking for a very easy but properly delicious supper? Try these Middle-Eastern inspired chicken wraps.\n', 30, 30, 4, 13),
(3, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pan-fried_gnocchi_with_36887\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/pan-fried_gnocchi_with_36887_16x9.jpg\n', 'Pan-fried gnocchi with broccoli pesto and grilled veg\n', ' Fast and tasty green veg - griddled for that smoky taste. The ready-made gnocchi are fried for extra crunch and served with a homemade chilli broccolli pesto.\n', 30, 10, 4, 15),
(4, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/vegan_banana_bread_37216\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/vegan_banana_bread_37216_16x9.jpg\n', 'Vegan banana bread\n', ' Here’s the vegan banana bread you’ve been searching for! Add some chopped pecan nuts if you like for a bit of crunch.\n \n Each serving provides 242kcal, 4g protein, 46g carbohydrate (of which 22g sugars), 15g fat (of which 2g saturates), 2g fibre and 0.4g salt.\n', 30, 120, 10, 8),
(5, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/potato_hash_with_tomato_35594\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/potato_hash_with_tomato_35594_16x9.jpg\n', 'Potato hash with tomatoes, pepper and kale\n', ' This easy one-pan supper has crispy potatoes and kale, juicy tomatoes and peppers, and set eggs with perfectly runny yolks.\n \n Each serving provides 480 kcal, 25g protein, 56g carbohydrates (of which 10.5g sugars), 15g fat (of which 4g saturates), 9.5g fibre and 1.1g salt.\n', 30, 90, 2, 11),
(6, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/tuscan_peasant_pot_soup_52268\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/tuscan_peasant_pot_soup_52268_16x9.jpg\n', 'Tuscan bacon and bean soup with wild garlic pesto\n', ' Pressure cooking creates an authentic Tuscan bean and bacon soup in minutes. \n \n Equipment and preparation: you will need a pressure cooker and a pestle and mortar\n', 30, 30, 4, 35),
(7, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spiced_roast_chicken_94425\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/spiced_roast_chicken_94425_16x9.jpg\n', 'Spiced roast chicken\n', ' Spice up on your Sunday roast with this Indian-influenced marinade and coconut milk gravy. \n', 90, 120, 4, 30),
(8, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/stir_fried_chicken_and_37476\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/stir_fried_chicken_and_37476_16x9.jpg\n', 'Stir-fried chicken and broccoli with noodles\n', ' Stir-fries are very flexible - throw in whatever vegetables you like into this easy sweet and savoury chicken supper.\n', 30, 30, 4, 20),
(9, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pot-roast_pork_enchaud_28198\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/pot-roast_pork_enchaud_28198_16x9.jpg\n', 'Pot-roast pork (Enchaud périgourdin)\n', ' I bought a couple of jars of Enchaud périgourdin in Périgueux market. It’s pork loin that is studded with garlic and pot-roasted with a small amount of stock and pig’s trotters, then left to go cold before being bottled. It’s designed to be thinly sliced and served with other cold meats, pâtés and pickles. I decided to create a version in which I stud the pork with plenty of garlic in the same way, wrap it in the skin to keep in the moisture and pot-roast it with lots of root vegetables for a deep winter flavour. \n', 120, 120, 6, 20),
(10, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/anda_paratha_62344\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/anda_paratha_62344_16x9.jpg\n', 'Anda paratha\n', ' This makes a great late evening snack or brunch dish with a kick! Make a batch and reheat for a quick early morning snack. \n', 30, 30, 6, 11),
(11, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/one_pan_breakfast_bowl_47359\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/one_pan_breakfast_bowl_47359_16x9.jpg\n', 'One-pan all-day breakfast\n', ' A hearty, low-calorie one-pan breakfast to wake you up and get your metabolism going. \n \n Each serving provides 455 kcal, 22.5g protein, 22g carbohydrates (of which 10.5g sugars), 23g fat (of which 7.5g saturates), 7.5g fibre and 2.3g salt. \n \n \n \n With a GI of 45 this meal is high protein, low GI.\n', 30, 90, 4, 11),
(12, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/duck_cottage_pie_32748\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/duck_cottage_pie_32748_16x9.jpg\n', 'Duck cottage pie (Parmentier de confit de canard)\n', ' Tom Kevill-Davis wrote a book called The Hungry Cyclist and he’s married to Aude Bonnetain, whose family makes excellent Burgundy in Auxey-Duresses. Her food is exceptional and a standout dish among the loyal grape pickers, who return year after year, is parmentier de confit de canard or duck cottage pie. Unctuous, filling and restorative, it has legendary status among the team.\n', 30, 120, 4, 21),
(13, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/american_style_pancakes_94634\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/american_style_pancakes_94634_16x9.jpg\n', 'American-style blueberry pancakes\n', ' An American classic, these fluffy blueberry pancakes make the perfect brunch and are served with maple butter. \n \n Try experimenting with the toppings of this American buttermilk pancake recipe by adding bacon, eggs, nuts, syrup or yoghurt. \n', 30, 30, 8, 14),
(14, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spaghettiallacarbona_86763\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/spaghettiallacarbona_86763_16x9.jpg\n', 'Rick Stein\'s spaghetti alla carbonara\n', ' Rick Stein\'s authentic spaghetti carbonara is easy, delicious and wonderfully creamy. But this recipe doesn\'t actually contain cream so more healthy! \n', 30, 30, 4, 9),
(15, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mushroom_stroganoff_with_83256\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mushroom_stroganoff_with_83256_16x9.jpg\n', 'Easy mushroom stroganoff\n', ' A vegetarian mushroom stroganoff that\'s as rich and delicious as its meaty cousin. This is designed to be a low cost recipe.\n', 30, 30, 4, 13),
(16, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/beetroot_chocolate_cake_82388\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/beetroot_chocolate_cake_82388_16x9.jpg\n', 'Beetroot chocolate cake \n', ' If you haven’t yet discovered the delicious and surprising combo of beetroot and chocolate cake, this is the perfect introductory recipe. Try it with a dollop of crème fraîche. \n', 30, 90, 6, 12),
(17, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/coconutfishcurry_89979\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/coconutfishcurry_89979_16x9.jpg\n', 'Coconut fish curry\n', ' A creamy fish curry with just enough spice, power it up with sweet potato and spinach to get you on your way to five a day. \n', 30, 30, 2, 19),
(18, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/low-cal_breakfast_bake_67023\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/low-cal_breakfast_bake_67023_16x9.jpg\n', 'Breakfast bake \n', ' This lower-calorie cooked breakfast is baked in the oven, so you can get on with your morning.\n \n Each serving provides 385 kcal, 36g protein, 31g carbohydrate (of which 9g sugars), 11.5g fat (of which 3.5g saturates), 8g fibre and 2.5g salt.\n', 30, 30, 2, 12),
(19, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/kombucha_49471\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/kombucha_49471_16x9.jpg\n', 'Kombucha \n', ' Kombucha is a delicious fermented drink. Try making it with green tea for another variation. \n \n Make sure you follow the instructions that come with your scoby. Please note that kombucha contains a tiny amount of alcohol.\n \n \n \n For this recipe you will need a 2 litre/3½ pint wide-mouthed clip-top jar, a very jug or bowl, a large measuring jug or bowl, a clean tightly woven muslin, a\n \n rubber band or string, a funnel and clip-top round glass bottles for decanting.\n', 30, NULL, 1, 5),
(20, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/smoky_bean_chipotle_stew_30894\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/smoky_bean_chipotle_stew_30894_16x9.jpg\n', 'Vegan chilli \n', ' This delicious and healthy vegan chilli recipe gets its smoky flavour from chipotle paste, made from smoked jalapeno peppers. You can use any tins of beans that you like, or even tinned lentils.\n \n This meal provides 501 kcal, 18g protein, 71g carbohydrate (of which 18g sugars), 16g fat (of which 3g saturates), 17g fibre and 1.4g salt per portion. \n', 30, 90, 4, 23),
(21, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chickpea_coconut_curry_49762\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chickpea_coconut_curry_49762_16x9.jpg\n', 'Chickpea coconut curry\n', ' Just five ingredients and one of them’s rice! Have this easy vegan chickpea curry on the table in less than 10 minutes.\n \n Each serving provides 501 kcal, 18g protein, 71.5g carbohydrates (of which 6g sugars), 13.5g fat (of which 7.5g saturates), 12g fibre and 0.6g salt.\n', 30, 10, 2, 7),
(22, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/eggy_bread_11076\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/eggy_bread_11076_16x9.jpg\n', 'Eggy bread\n', ' Rachel Phipps\' quick and cheap eggy bread is great for breakfast or an afternoon snack. Serve with your favourite sauce.\n \n Each serving provides 372 kcal, 19g protein, 47g carbohydrate (of which 3g sugars), 12g fat (of which 2g saturates), 3g fibre and 1.3g salt.\n', 30, 10, 1, 8),
(23, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mattar_paneer_38293\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mattar_paneer_38293_16x9.jpg\n', 'Matar paneer\n', ' This is a classic vegetarian curry of Indian cheese and peas cooked in a tomato-based sauce. Frying the cheese until golden makes a big difference to the flavour and texture of the curry so don\'t be tempted to skip that step.\n', 30, 90, 4, 21),
(24, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/easy_chickpea_and_71540\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/easy_chickpea_and_71540_16x9.jpg\n', 'Easy chickpea and squash curry\n', ' When you want a healthy, cheap dinner, this easy vegan curry recipe is the one. Serves four or freezes really well. \n', 30, 90, 2, 16),
(25, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mexicansweetcornpanc_89498\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mexicansweetcornpanc_89498_16x9.jpg\n', 'Mexican sweetcorn pancakes, poached eggs and salsa\n', ' A healthy breakfast doesn\'t need to taste boring - add zing to your morning with salsa and sweetcorn pancakes.\n', 30, 10, 2, 19),
(26, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/gnocchi_pasta_bake_51351\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/gnocchi_pasta_bake_51351_16x9.jpg\n', 'One-pan gnocchi bake\n', ' A gnocchi bake is a super comforting and easy one-pan family dinner. A bit like a pasta bake just using a bag of gnocchi and some veggies straight out of the freezer.\n \n The great thing about only using one pan is you hardly have to wash up!\n \n \n', 30, 30, 4, 15),
(27, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/butternut_and_sweet_04563\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/butternut_and_sweet_04563_16x9.jpg\n', 'Butternut and sweet potato curry\n', ' This is a rambunctiously vibrant vegan curry, both to look at and eat. It is rich, sweet and hearty, with tomatoes providing a balancing acidity and the curry paste bringing uncompromising fire. Of course chillies do vary in heat, so if you’re after something a little less passage-clearing, use two rather than three, and if you want to go milder still, simply de-seed the chillies. Having said that, cooking with chillies always has a touch of roulette about it. \n', 30, 90, 4, 24),
(28, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mushrooms_leeks_and_90926\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mushrooms_leeks_and_90926_16x9.jpg\n', 'Mushrooms, leeks and fried eggs on toast\n', ' Mushrooms and leeks on toast are a great way to eat more veg for breakfast, brunch or a light lunch. \n \n Each serving provides 459 kcal, 17g protein, 23g carbohydrates (of which 5g sugars), 32g fat (of which 15g saturates), 6g fibre and 1.7g salt.\n', 30, 10, 1, 11),
(29, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/vegan_fried_breakfast_34182\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/vegan_fried_breakfast_34182_16x9.jpg\n', 'Vegan fried breakfast\n', ' This vegan full English breakfast is the ultimate start to the day. Vegan sausage, mushrooms, scrambled tofu and more. The recipe makes twice as much seitan as you need, but it will keep in the fridge for a little while. \n \n Each serving provides 924 kcal, 33g protein, 102g carbohydrates (of which 17g sugars), 41g fat (of which 7g saturates), 17g fibre and 3.5g salt. \n', NULL, 120, 4, 46),
(30, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/vegetarian_shepherds_pie_73637\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/vegetarian_shepherds_pie_73637_16x9.jpg\n', 'Veggie shepherd’s pie\n', ' This simple, hearty, vegetarian shepherd’s pie is packed full of healthy vegetables and lentils. Omit the Worcestershire sauce and Parmesan to make it a hearty vegetarian dinner.\n \n This meal provides 416 kcal, 17g protein, 68g carbohydrate (of which 19g sugars), 6g fat (of which 2.5g saturates), 15g fibre and 1.5g salt per portion.\n \n \n', 30, 90, 4, 28),
(31, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/salad_of_peppers_18285\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/salad_of_peppers_18285_16x9.jpg\n', 'Salad of peppers, anchovies and hard-boiled eggs (salade collioure)\n', ' In Collioure, I quickly came to realise that this little salad sums up what’s best about French Mediterranean cuisine. It’s the sort of thing you can rustle up so easily, whether as an appetiser, a simple first course or light lunch and everyone will love it. By the way, the anchovies in the Languedoc-Roussillon region are really quite special. \n', 30, 30, 4, 11),
(32, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/eggs_benedict_10471\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/eggs_benedict_10471_16x9.jpg\n', 'Eggs Benedict\n', ' Eggs Benedict is the perfect weekend breakfast or brunch.  \n \n Homemade hollandaise sauce is much easier to prepare than you may think and beats any kind of shop-bought variety.\n \n \n \n This recipe allows you to make six perfect poached eggs ready to serve at the same time.  It\'s all in the prep!\n', 30, 30, 6, 16),
(33, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/gnocchi_with_crispy_19660\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/gnocchi_with_crispy_19660_16x9.jpg\n', 'Gnocchi with crispy bacon and spinach pesto\n', ' Gnocchi makes an easy-peasy 10-minute dinner. It\'s so simple to give homemade pesto a healthy boost using fresh spinach.\n \n For this recipe you will need a mini food processor or a blender.\n \n \n \n Each serving provides 631 kcal, 17g protein, 74g carbohydrates (of which 1g sugars), 28g fat (of which 10.5g saturates), 6g fibre and 3.3g salt.\n', 30, 10, 2, 8),
(34, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/keylimepie_93185\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/keylimepie_93185_16x9.jpg\n', 'Key lime pie\n', ' This classic American dessert is sure to impress, perfect when you want something different for a dinner party!\n', 120, 30, 8, 13),
(35, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/onion_bhajis_60658\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/onion_bhajis_60658_16x9.jpg\n', 'Mini onion bhajis\n', ' These mini onion bhajis are quick to make and such a treat fresh from the pan. Try them as a snack or alongside a curry. Any extras can be frozen and reheated in the oven.\n', 30, 10, 12, 13),
(36, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/membrillo_and_stilton_28987\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/membrillo_and_stilton_28987_16x9.jpg\n', 'Stilton and butternut squash quiche with roast sprouts\n', ' This Stilton and butternut squash quiche makes for an unforgettable vegetarian Christmas. Especially served with golden sprouts. \n', 120, 120, 6, 23),
