(83, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pancakes_egg_hollandaise_34409\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/pancakes_egg_hollandaise_34409_16x9.jpg\n', 'Pancakes with poached egg, ham and easy hollandaise\n', ' Treat someone (and yourself!) with this luxurious pancake recipe with easy hollandaise sauce. Look for the best quality ham – or you could use some shredded ham hock.\n', 30, 10, 4, 19),
(84, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/roasted_vegetable_quiche_25657\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/roasted_vegetable_quiche_25657_16x9.jpg\n', 'Roasted vegetable quiche\n', ' Filled with colourful chunky vegetables and large enough to serve a crowd, this would make a decorative addition to an Easter feast. Roasting the vegetables, and including Gruyère with its distinctive flavour, ensures that it is very moreish too.\n \n For this recipe you will need a 28cm/11in loose-bottomed  fluted tart tin and some baking beans.\n', 90, 120, 10, 12),
(85, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/low-fat_chicken_curry_88832\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/low-fat_chicken_curry_88832_16x9.jpg\n', 'Healthy chicken curry\n', ' Marinating the meat helps your get ahead with this jalfrezi-style healthy chicken curry. It\'s packed with veggies and served with a fresh salad. Serve with brown basmati rice.\n \n This meal provides 164 kcal, 21g protein, 13.7g carbohydrate (of which 11g sugars), 2.9g fat (of which 0.5g saturates), 4.1g fibre and 1.4g salt per portion.\n', 30, 30, 4, 29),
(86, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/meatballsandtomatosa_90717\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/meatballsandtomatosa_90717_16x9.jpg\n', 'Meatball sandwich\n', ' Sometimes all you need is a really good sandwich and this one with homemade meatballs and tomato sauce is just the trick. \n', 30, 30, 1, 13),
(87, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/1_hoisin_spinach_and_egg_86057\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/1_hoisin_spinach_and_egg_86057_16x9.jpg\n', '£1 hoisin, spinach and egg noodles\n', ' Hoisin is the secret to creating an easy, no-cook Chinese sauce to serve with these cheap and cheerful noodles. Cooking the noodles and spinach in the same pan helps cut down on washing up, too. Make this dish for less than £1 per portion.\n \n Each serving provides 385 kcal, 18g protein, 56g carbohydrate (of which 8g sugars), 8.5g fat (of which 2g saturates), 5.5g fibre and 3.5g salt.\n', 30, 30, 2, 8),
(88, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/steakandkidneypuddin_93128\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/steakandkidneypuddin_93128_16x9.jpg\n', 'Steak and kidney pudding\n', ' Suet pastry filled with tender steak and kidney in a rich gravy - a British classic pudding to be proud of. \n', 90, 120, 6, 16),
(89, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/treacle_pudding_80920\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/treacle_pudding_80920_16x9.jpg\n', 'Treacle pudding\n', ' A simple steamed syrup sponge, treacle pudding is guaranteed to please. Steam traditionally or microwave in 5 minutes.\n', 30, 120, 6, 7),
(90, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/bunting_cake_35577\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/bunting_cake_35577_16x9.jpg\n', 'Bunting cake\n', ' This charming colourful sponge cake is decorated with beautiful bunting, easily made with straws and scraps of cute fabric.  \n \n Equipment and preparation: You will need two lengths of doweling rod, assorted ribbon and thread, and an electric mixer.\n', 30, 90, 8, 16),
(91, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/flourlesschocolateca_93580\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/flourlesschocolateca_93580_16x9.jpg\n', 'Flourless chocolate cake\n', ' A truly moreish gluten-free chocolate cake, pile this one high with fruit and cream. That\'s what the sunken middle was made for.\n', 30, 90, 1, 11),
(92, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/punjabi_chicken_curry_44800\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/punjabi_chicken_curry_44800_16x9.jpg\n', 'Punjabi chicken curry \n', ' This super-easy, hearty chicken curry layers up earthy spices, including cardamom and turmeric with zingy root ginger and fresh coriander leaves. \n', 30, 90, 4, 20),
(93, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/beachside_paella_41859\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/beachside_paella_41859_16x9.jpg\n', 'Beachside paella\n', ' We cooked this on a beach in Northumberland and some said it was the best paella they’d ever tasted – dieting or not. You know what? We have to agree.358 calories per portion\n', 30, 30, 6, 28),
(94, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/red_lentil_and_aubergine_33187\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/red_lentil_and_aubergine_33187_16x9.jpg\n', 'Vegetarian moussaka \n', ' A really easy gluten-free and vegetarian moussaka is the comfort food every veggie needs in their life. \n \n Each serving provides 347 kcal, 17g protein, 45g carbohydrates (of which 11g sugars), 9g fat (of which 5g saturates), 9g fibre and 1.1g salt.\n', 30, 90, 4, 17),
(95, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/beef_and_pork_meatballs_23514\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/beef_and_pork_meatballs_23514_16x9.jpg\n', 'Meatballs in a spicy tomato sauce (Boles de picolat)\n', ' This recipe came from a stall in Prades market where they were cooking boles meatballs in a huge paella pan. They were fabulous – beef and pork meatballs flavoured with cinnamon and piment d’Espelette in an exquisite tomato sauce with green olives, haricot beans and bacon. I thought there might be too much meat in the dish, but not at all.\n', 30, 120, 4, 29),
(96, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/shakshuka_with_28705\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/shakshuka_with_28705_16x9.jpg\n', 'Shakshuka with flatbreads\n', ' Shakshuka is a tasty and healthy dish for an easy midweek dinner or weekend brunch. Making your own flatbreads is very simple and they are much nicer than the tortilla wraps found in most supermarkets.\n', 30, 90, 4, 33),
(97, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/1_mixed_vegetable_and_84703\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/1_mixed_vegetable_and_84703_16x9.jpg\n', 'Mixed vegetable and almond biryani\n', ' This gently spiced biryani costs just £1 per portion. It makes use of that packet of chopped mixed veg languishing at the bottom of your freezer. Enjoy it by itself with a dollop of yogurt and mango chutney, or as part of a feast – it\'s particularly delicious with aloo gosht.\n \n Each serving provides 429 kcal, 10.5g protein, 70g carbohydrate (of which 5.5g sugars), 11.5g fat (of which 1g saturates), 2g fibre and 2.9g salt.\n', 30, 90, 4, 14),
(98, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spicy_potato_wraps_01639\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/spicy_potato_wraps_01639_16x9.jpg\n', 'Spicy potato wraps\n', ' These tasty wraps are a great way to use up any leftover potatoes, but they work particularly well with boiled or baked spuds. Making your own tortillas is trouble-free and very cheap but you can buy them if you prefer.\n', 90, 10, 3, 21),
(99, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/lemon_and_blueberry_28793\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/lemon_and_blueberry_28793_16x9.jpg\n', 'Lemon and blueberry yoghurt pots\n', ' A low-fat dessert very similar to an Eton mess. Summer on a spoon!\n \n Each serving provides 128 kcal, 8g protein, 21g carbohydrate, 1g fat,1g fibre.\n', 30, 10, 4, 9),
(100, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/scrambledeggandtoast_75736\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/scrambledeggandtoast_75736_16x9.jpg\n', 'Scrambled egg and toast with smoked salmon\n', ' This breakfast is the perfect brain food for when you have a challenging day ahead, plus it\'s super easy to make. \n \n Each serving provides 605kcal, 33g protein, 17g carbohydrate (of which 2g sugars), 44g fat (of which 21g saturates), 2g fibre and 3g salt.\n', 30, 10, 1, 7),
(101, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/stuffed_vegetables_56352\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/stuffed_vegetables_56352_16x9.jpg\n', 'Stuffed vegetables\n', ' When we were filming in Greece, stuffed vegetables was our favourite dish. It all stemmed from a brief lunch stop at the little fishing village of Astakos, where we asked what was for lunch at the first quayside café we came to. They said stuffed tomatoes and peppers, which had just come out of the oven. Straight from the oven when you are ravenously hungry is perfect. \n \n This meal, if served as 10 portions, provides 249kcal, 5g protein, 39g carbohydrate (of which 6g sugars),	7.5g fat (of which 1.5g saturates), 4g fibre and 0.2g salt per portion.\n', 30, 120, 8, 19),
(102, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/sausage_and_gnocchi_bake_80924\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/sausage_and_gnocchi_bake_80924_16x9.jpg\n', 'Sausage bake with gnocchi\n', ' This easy sausage bake is made with gnocchi rather than pasta. Roasted gnocchi is magical – while the inside stays light and fluffy, the outside goes crisp and golden, like mini roast potatoes.\n \n Each serving provides 600 kcal, 24g protein, 47g carbohydrates (of which 10g sugars), 33.5g fat (of which 12g saturates), 8g fibre and 1.8g salt.\n', 30, 30, 2, 11),
(103, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/coleslaw_68108\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/coleslaw_68108_16x9.jpg\n', 'Coleslaw\n', ' When a coleslaw recipe is this easy, you need never buy it ready-made again. Feel free to try adding other crunchy veg like fennel, celery or celeriac. You can stir in fresh herbs or swap the mustard for a chilli sauce. \n', 30, NULL, 4, 11),
(104, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/christmas_pudding_41498\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/christmas_pudding_41498_16x9.jpg\n', 'Christmas pudding\n', ' Get motivated in November to make your Christmas pudding to have it mature in time for Christmas.\n \n Equipment and preparation: You will need a 1.2 litre/2 pint pudding basin, baking paper, foil and kitchen string.\n', NULL, 120, 1, 18),
(105, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/veggie_pizzas_63934\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/veggie_pizzas_63934_16x9.jpg\n', 'Veggie pizza\n', ' Who said pizza was unhealthy? These veggie pizzas pack winning flavour combinations plus your five-a-day. \n', 120, 90, 4, 23),
(106, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/hearty_wholewheat_pasta_66804\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/hearty_wholewheat_pasta_66804_16x9.jpg\n', 'Hearty wholewheat pasta with Brussels sprouts, cheese and potato\n', ' Don’t be modishly alarmed by the double-carb combo: it can be an alcohol-sopping salve, much appreciated at this time of year. Besides, it is important to remember that the original predates central heating.\n', 30, 90, 8, 13),
(107, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/masala_omelette_with_80543\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/masala_omelette_with_80543_16x9.jpg\n', 'Masala omelette with parathas\n', ' A spicy masala omelette is my ‘go to’ weekend brunch. My mother always made it for us in India. The combination of ground spices, chillies and eggs just works. It\'s lightly crisp around the edges but moist, with a fiery chilli kick. It\'s great served with parathas. \n', 30, 30, 2, 17),
(108, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pakistani_spicy_potatoes_93471\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/pakistani_spicy_potatoes_93471_16x9.jpg\n', 'Pakistani spicy potatoes (aloo bhujia)\n', ' This is gorgeous served simply with rice but also tastes great as a side dish for meat and fish. \n', 30, 30, 3, 19),
(109, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/veggie_korma_naan_16659\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/veggie_korma_naan_16659_16x9.jpg\n', 'Veggie korma with naan\n', ' Vegetable kormas can be quick, easy, cheap to make. Kerry makes easy naans with her children to go with the lovely, mild veggie curry.\n \n', 30, 30, 4, 22),
(110, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/lamb_bhuna_60540\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/lamb_bhuna_60540_16x9.jpg\n', 'Lamb bhuna\n', ' Neck of lamb is a great cut of meat to use in this easy lamb curry as it has a rich taste and cooks quickly for a shortcut slow-braised curry that\'s worth every calorie. \n \n Each serving provides 752 kcal, 56g protein, 52g carbohydrate, 34g fat, 6g fibre.\n', 30, 120, 4, 23);
INSERT INTO `recipe_info` (`recipe_id`, `recipe_url`, `image_url`, `title`, `description`, `preparation_time`, `cook_time`, `serving_count`, `ingredient_count`) VALUES
(111, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/vegan_shepherds_pie_05111\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/vegan_shepherds_pie_05111_16x9.jpg\n', 'Vegan shepherd’s pie \n', ' This delicious, savoury vegan shepherd\'s pie freezes very well, so make in individual portions if you prefer, or freeze the leftovers. The secret ingredient is nutritional yeast, a great vegan ingredient that lends a cheesy flavour to the mash topping. Serve with lots of freshly cooked green vegetables.\n \n Each serving provides 441 kcal, 18g protein, 54g carbohydrate (of which 10g sugars), 13g fat (of which 2g saturates), 12g fibre and 1g salt.\n \n \n', 90, 120, 6, 26),
(112, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/marinatedbeetroot_67843\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/marinatedbeetroot_67843_16x9.jpg\n', 'Marinated beetroot\n', ' A great little make-ahead side dish that would work well with roasts and veggie feasts.  Not quite pickled, these beetroot are still sweet but also a little sour.\n', NULL, 120, 4, 9),
(113, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/cornish_gypsy_eggs_45609\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/cornish_gypsy_eggs_45609_16x9.jpg\n', 'Gypsy eggs \n', ' Baked eggs in a rich tomato and chorizo sauce makes a brilliant brunch dish. Top with crispy Parma ham and Parmesan for ultimate indulgence. \n', 30, 30, 4, 17),
(114, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/veggie_slow-cooker_curry_48226\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/veggie_slow-cooker_curry_48226_16x9.jpg\n', 'Veggie slow cooker curry\n', ' Just a few minutes precooking and this rich tasting slow-cooker veg curry can be quickly assembled – serve with basmati rice, plain yoghurt and assorted chutneys and pickles.\n \n Each serving provides 248 kcal, 6g protein, 38g carbohydrates (of which 16.5g sugars), 6.5g fat (of which 0.5g saturates), 7.5g fibre and 1.6g salt.\n \n \n', 30, 120, 4, 18),
(115, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/eggs_benedict_florentine_33122\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/eggs_benedict_florentine_33122_16x9.jpg\n', 'Eggs Benedict Florentine \n', ' Mary Berry\'s perfect eggs benedict florentine combines the two ultimate brunches for a perfect start to the weekend. \n \n Watch Mary maker her  Hollandaise sauce here.\n \n \n \n \n', 30, 30, 4, 11),
(116, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/steamed_lemon_sponge_90062\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/steamed_lemon_sponge_90062_16x9.jpg\n', 'Steamed lemon sponge puddings with custard\n', ' Light as air and deliciously sweet, these individual sponge puddings are comfort food to impress.\n \n For this recipe you will need four individual pudding moulds, a steamer and kitchen string.\n', 30, 30, 4, 17),
(117, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chocolate_brownie_64092\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chocolate_brownie_64092_16x9.jpg\n', 'Chocolate brownie meringue cake with raspberry cream\n', ' This heavenly dessert – gooey brownie and squidgy meringue sandwiched with whipped cream and raspberries – is perfect for any celebration.\n', 30, 90, 16, 15),
(118, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/buckwheat_pancakes_with_04857\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/buckwheat_pancakes_with_04857_16x9.jpg\n', 'Buckwheat pancakes with mushrooms and egg\n', ' This recipe comes from the town of Salers, famous for its cheese. Salers cheese is similar to Cantal but is made only from the milk of the cows grazing on its mountain pastures in the summer. The town itself is extraordinary. No part of France is really that secret, but when I arrived in Salers on a sunny morning it felt like I’d just landed somewhere in Ruritania. For lunch, we all ordered these hearty, yeasted pancakes.\n', 120, 30, 4, 19),
(119, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/nimki_03944\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/nimki_03944_16x9.jpg\n', 'Nimki\n', ' These spicy pastry snacks are rolled and folded with ghee and taste wonderful with a cup of chai masala. \n', 90, 90, 10, 10),
(120, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/fattoush_86811\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/fattoush_86811_16x9.jpg\n', 'Fattoush\n', ' This salad is all about sourness. The combination of lemon and sumac really packs a punch. Great with a barbecue.\n', 30, NULL, 4, 16),
(121, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chocolate_and_hazelnut_38207\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chocolate_and_hazelnut_38207_16x9.jpg\n', 'Chocolate hazelnut cake \n', ' We made this as a birthday cake for Italy, which celebrated the 150th anniversary of its unification in 2011. Gianduia is a speciality of the Piedmont region and it’s a mixture of ground hazelnuts and chocolate.\n', 90, 90, 10, 9),
(122, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/ginger_and_orange_cake_77943\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/ginger_and_orange_cake_77943_16x9.jpg\n', 'Ginger and marmalade loaf cake \n', ' This light, easy-to-make ginger loaf cake has an extra layer of flavour thanks to the addition of orange marmalade and zest.  \n', 30, 90, 8, 10),
(123, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/courgette_and_lemon_44907\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/courgette_and_lemon_44907_16x9.jpg\n', 'Courgette and lemon risotto\n', ' This gorgeous summertime risotto is a favourite with kids and the cold leftovers can be used to make tasty arancini.\n \n Each serving provides 440kcal, 11g protein, 42g carbohydrate (of which 2g sugars), 21g fat (of which 13g saturates), 1.5g fibre and 1.4g salt.\n \n \n', 30, 30, 4, 14),
(124, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mince_and_dumplings_47431\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mince_and_dumplings_47431_16x9.jpg\n', 'Mince and dumplings\n', ' Embrace autumn with a great, big hug of a dish: comforting mince and dumplings. \n', 30, 90, 6, 18),
(125, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/aubergine_parmigiana_57566\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/aubergine_parmigiana_57566_16x9.jpg\n', 'Aubergine parmigiana\n', ' Donal\'s aubergine parmigiana is so easy to make and tastes wonderful. It\'s simpler than a lasagne and lighter, too. The tomato sauce can be doubled and frozen for another easy dinner. \n', 30, 90, 4, 13),
(126, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/almond_lentil_stew_69086\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/almond_lentil_stew_69086_16x9.jpg\n', 'Almond lentil stew\n', ' This easy vegetarian lentil stew is served with cherry tomatoes and cinnamon-flavoured almonds.\n \n This meal is low calorie  and if served as four portions provides 351 kcal, 20g protein, 37g carbohydrate (of which 7.5g sugars), 14g fat (of which 1.5g saturates), 11.5g fibre and 1.9g salt per portion.\n', 30, 90, 3, 15),
(127, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/midweek_chicken_korma_82829\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/midweek_chicken_korma_82829_16x9.jpg\n', 'Easy chicken korma\n', ' This chicken korma is full of flavour and exciting ingredients but is quick and easy to prepare, making it an ideal midweek dinner. It is also great for a low-calorie meal option.\n \n Each serving provides 499 kcal, 46g protein, 53g carbohydrates (of which 7.5g sugars), 10g fat (of which 3.5g saturates), 6g fibre and 1.3g salt. \n', 30, 90, 4, 19),
(128, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/butternut_squash_pasta_32947\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/butternut_squash_pasta_32947_16x9.jpg\n', 'Butternut squash pasta\n', ' An easy butternut squash pasta sauce for any pasta, but ideally tagliatelle. \n', 30, 90, 2, 15),
(129, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/peri-peri_chicken_79598\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/peri-peri_chicken_79598_16x9.jpg\n', 'Peri-peri chicken\n', ' A tasty chicken and spicy rice dish to rival your peri-peri chicken shop! The slaw can work as side for other dishes too.\n \n Each serving provides 614 kcal, 41g protein, 50g carbohydrate, 26g fat,7g fibre.\n', 30, 30, 4, 27),
(130, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/vegetable_garden_risotto_60989\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/vegetable_garden_risotto_60989_16x9.jpg\n', 'Broad bean risotto\n', ' A simple vegetarian risotto by the Hairy Bikers that uses wonderfully fresh British vegetables and herbs.\n', 30, 30, 4, 23),
(131, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/butternut_squash_and_46813\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/butternut_squash_and_46813_16x9.jpg\n', 'Slow cooker vegetarian hotpot \n', ' This slow-cooker vegetarian stew with fluffy dumplings, is a cheap and easy recipe. To make it vegan, use vegetable suet in the dumplings instead of butter. This dish is perfect for batch cooking, just divide it up into indiviudal portions and you will always have warming stew at your fingertips, check the tips section for freezing instructions. \n \n Equipment and preparation: For this recipe you will need a 6.5 litre/11½ pint slow-cooker. \n \n \n \n This meal provides 629 kcal, 13g protein, 79g carbohydrate (of which 24g sugars), 29g fat (of which 11g saturates), 16g fibre and 1.8g salt per portion.\n', 30, 120, 4, 19),
