(329, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/sweet_potato_brownies_66025\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/sweet_potato_brownies_66025_16x9.jpg\n', 'Sweet potato brownies\n', ' These brownies are packed with caramelised sweet potato for a sweet, fudgy texture. \n', 30, 120, 12, 22),
(330, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/tagliatelle_with_23536\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/tagliatelle_with_23536_16x9.jpg\n', 'Tagliatelle with mushrooms and pancetta\n', ' A simple pasta dish made with porcini and wild mushrooms for an extra special touch. Stir in a little cream at the end if you are feeling indulgent.\n', 30, 10, 2, 12),
(331, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/apple_and_wensleydale_16189\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/apple_and_wensleydale_16189_16x9.jpg\n', 'Apple and Wensleydale pie\n', ' There’s a saying in Yorkshire that ‘apple pie without cheese is like a kiss without a squeeze’. I couldn’t agree more – tangy, salty cheese and sweet apple go beautifully together. I like to use a mixture of cooking and eating apples in this pie, in order to create a varied, interesting texture.\n', 90, 30, 6, 8),
(332, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spaghetti_and_meatballs_69603\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/spaghetti_and_meatballs_69603_16x9.jpg\n', 'Spaghetti and meatballs\n', ' A simple tomato sauce with lots of flavour is perfect for spaghetti and meatballs. A weeknight classic. This is designed to be a low cost recipe.\n', 30, 90, 4, 14),
(333, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/dark_and_sumptuous_53597\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/dark_and_sumptuous_53597_16x9.jpg\n', 'Dark and sumptuous chocolate cake\n', ' A vegan chocolate cake to die for from Nigella Lawson\'s Simply Nigella.\n \n For this recipe you will need a leakproof 20cm/8in springform cake tin.\n', 30, 90, 10, 17),
(334, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/sticky_lamb_buns_with_a_40943\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/sticky_lamb_buns_with_a_40943_16x9.jpg\n', 'Sticky lamb buns with pickled cucumber relish\n', ' A great recipe for using up leftover roast lamb. Double the quantities to serve at small parties.\n', 90, 30, 4, 15),
(335, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/hoisin_salmon_with_44468\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/hoisin_salmon_with_44468_16x9.jpg\n', 'Hoisin salmon with broccoli and noodles \n', ' Hoisin is a spicy-sweet sauce made out of soya-bean paste, chillies and Chinese five spice. This salmon dish is suitable for a low-calorie diet of 1200–1500 calories a day.  \n \n Each serving provides 439 kcal, 32g protein, 32g carbohydrates (of which 7g sugars), 19g fat (of which 3.5g saturates), 4.5g fibre and 1.2g salt. \n', 30, 30, 4, 8),
(336, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/roti_31237\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/roti_31237_16x9.jpg\n', 'Roti\n', ' An authentic roti bread recipe, brilliant to serve with curries, making a good alternative to rice.\n', 90, 30, 6, 4),
(337, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/berry_banana_smoothie_16261\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/berry_banana_smoothie_16261_16x9.jpg\n', 'Healthy berry banana smoothie\n', ' An easy, dairy-free healthy smoothie you can whizz up in seconds, full of fruit, fibre and healthy fats.\n \n Each serving provides 678 kcal, 18g protein, 64.5g carbohydrates (of which 24g sugars), 35.5g fat (of which 5.5g saturates), 13.5g fibre and 0.3g salt.\n', 30, NULL, 1, 7),
(338, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spicyblackbeanquesad_92202\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/spicyblackbeanquesad_92202_16x9.jpg\n', 'Spicy black bean quesadilla\n', ' Quesadillas are just fancy for flattened, fried wraps - black beans and cheese fill these with an avocado side salad.\n', 30, 10, 2, 17),
(339, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/panettone_07948\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/panettone_07948_16x9.jpg\n', 'Easy panettone\n', ' This is a ‘quick’ panettone recipe which delivers on flavour and texture. It’s my go-to for a last-minute Christmas cake!\n \n For this recipe you will need a 18cm/7in deep cake tin.\n \n \n', 120, 90, 8, 17),
(340, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/baked_pappardelle_with_21046\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/baked_pappardelle_with_21046_16x9.jpg\n', 'Baked pappardelle with pancetta and porcini\n', ' Bake pasta for a bubbling sharing-at-the-table dish. Can you resist the aroma of cheese, pancetta and porcini?\n', 30, 90, 2, 9),
(341, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/roastturkeyandstuffi_71053\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/roastturkeyandstuffi_71053_16x9.jpg\n', 'Gordon Ramsay\'s roast turkey crown\n', ' Gordon Ramsay shows you how to roast turkey crown with a herb butter, stuffing and delicious creamy gravy. This turkey crown recipe is fit for a king. Calculate your exact turkey crown cooking times with our roast calculator.\n', 120, 120, 6, 28),
(342, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/orange_cake_57974\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/orange_cake_57974_16x9.jpg\n', 'Orange cake\n', ' This cake is best made the day before serving, and will keep in an airtight tin in a cool place for up to 5 days. \n', 30, 90, 12, 6),
(343, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/tuna_rocket_and_lemon_95118\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/tuna_rocket_and_lemon_95118_16x9.jpg\n', 'Pasta with tuna and rocket\n', ' This tuna pasta recipe is just as good cold as it is hot, so use any leftovers to make packed lunches. This is designed to be a low cost recipe.\n', 30, 30, 4, 9),
(344, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/roastcodwithalemonga_3477\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/roastcodwithalemonga_3477_16x9.jpg\n', 'Roast cod with a lemon, garlic and parsley crust\n', ' The delicate flavour of cod is wonderfully paired with lemon, garlic and parsley in this simple dish.\n \n This meal provides 322 kcal, 33g protein, 16g carbohydrate (of which 0.6g sugars), 14g fat (of which 8g saturates), 0.6g fibre and 0.9g salt per portion.\n', 30, 30, 4, 11);
INSERT INTO `recipe_info` (`recipe_id`, `recipe_url`, `image_url`, `title`, `description`, `preparation_time`, `cook_time`, `serving_count`, `ingredient_count`) VALUES
(345, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/lemon_and_ricotta_tart_44080\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/lemon_and_ricotta_tart_44080_16x9.jpg\n', 'Lemon and ricotta tart\n', ' This easy lemon tart is delicious served on its own or with roasted pears.\n', 30, 90, 8, 8),
(346, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/one_pot_prawn_spinach_81145\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/one_pot_prawn_spinach_81145_16x9.jpg\n', 'One pot prawn, spinach and tomato pasta \n', ' This prawn pasta is so incredibly quick and easy to make that you might find yourself having it every week. \n', 30, 30, 1, 11),
(347, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/beef_in_oyster_sauce_14507\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/beef_in_oyster_sauce_14507_16x9.jpg\n', 'Beef in oyster sauce\n', ' Try Ken Hom\'s beef in oyster sauce recipe for a Chinese takeaway classic, served with spicy salad.\n', 30, 10, 4, 24),
(348, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/sardine_beccafico_51534\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/sardine_beccafico_51534_16x9.jpg\n', 'Sardine beccafico\n', ' Enjoy Mediterranean flavours with this summery starter of stuffed baked sardines – ready to eat in just 20 minutes.\n', 30, 10, 6, 15),
(349, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chinese_sweetcorn_and_18611\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chinese_sweetcorn_and_18611_16x9.jpg\n', 'Leftover chicken and sweetcorn noodle soup \n', ' Reduce your food waste with this tasty leftover chicken noodle soup that makes great use of a roast chicken carcass. \n \n Watch the video for three ways to use up leftover roast chicken. Get the spiced chicken fajitas recipe here or find the chicken and mustard hotpot recipe here.\n', 30, 90, 2, 11),
(350, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/red_lentil_squash_and_72513\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/red_lentil_squash_and_72513_16x9.jpg\n', 'Red lentil and butternut squash soup\n', ' A thick, warming vegan lentil soup made with just three ingredients plus stock and seasoning. It\'s vegan and gluten-free too.\n \n For this recipe you will need a blender.\n', 30, 30, 4, 10),
(351, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/hotchocolate_81425\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/hotchocolate_81425_16x9.jpg\n', 'Hot chocolate\n', ' The Hairy Bikers show you how to make a creamy cup of hot chocolate, perfect for a cold winter’s day.\n', 30, 10, 4, 7),
(352, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/gnocchiallarrabbiata_85118\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/gnocchiallarrabbiata_85118_16x9.jpg\n', 'Spicy tomato sauce with gnocchi\n', ' Ready-made gnocchi in a spicy tomato sauce makes a change from pasta and is just as easy to prepare.\n', 30, 30, 1, 11),
(353, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/vietnamese_beef_and_57283\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/vietnamese_beef_and_57283_16x9.jpg\n', 'Vietnamese beef and lettuce wraps\n', ' Try serving strips of steak on lettuce with a sharp, sweet blend of Vietnamese flavours. Use a lean cut of beef such as rump or flank steak that\'s packed full of flavour and low in fat.\n', 120, 30, 4, 28),
(354, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/freezer_oaty_bar_14307\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/freezer_oaty_bar_14307_16x9.jpg\n', 'Oaty bars\n', ' Using peanut butter instead of butter means less fat and more protein than traditional flapjacks.\n \n Each serving provides 136 kcal, 3g protein, 16g carbohydrates (of which 10g sugars), 6g fat (of which 1g saturates), 2g fibre and trace salt.\n', 120, 10, 24, 10),
(355, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/easy_beef_stir-fry_84749\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/easy_beef_stir-fry_84749_16x9.jpg\n', 'Easy beef stir-fry\n', ' This easy beef stir-fry from Eat Well for Less is perfect for feeding family and friends. \n \n Each serving provides 484 kcal, 28g protein, 63g carbohydrates (of which 4g sugars), 12.5g fat (of which 3g saturates), 5g fibre and 1.5g salt.\n', 30, 30, 6, 16),
(356, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/sweetpotatowedges_83345\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/sweetpotatowedges_83345_16x9.jpg\n', 'Sweet potato wedges\n', ' Sweet potato wedges make a great alternative to potato and count as one of your 5-a-day.\n \n These wedges provide 229 kcal, 2g protein, 30g carbohydrate (of which 8g sugars), 11g fat (of which 2g saturates), 5g fibre and 0.2g salt per portion.\n', 30, 30, 4, 6),
(357, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/beef_sukiyaki_84557\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p01t7nnh.jpg\n', 'Beef sukiyaki \n', ' Kobe beef is said to be the best quality wagyu (‘Japanese cow’) in the world. But if you can’t source kobe, any good-quality beef will do the trick for this delicious Japanese stew.\n', 30, 30, 4, 20),
(358, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/tomatorisotto_92965\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/tomatorisotto_92965_16x9.jpg\n', 'Tomato risotto\n', ' A beautiful summer vegetable risotto with tomatoes, squash and fennel. Go the whole hog and make Raymond\'s tomato essence.\n', 30, 90, 2, 20),
(359, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spicedoatbiscuits_70435\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/spicedoatbiscuits_70435_16x9.jpg\n', 'Spiced oat cookies\n', ' At last! A sugar-free cookie! Tender, oaty and gently spiced, you\'ll never miss the sugar.\n \n Each cookie provides 82 kcal, 1g protein, 7g carbohydrate (of which 0.5g sugars), 5.5g fat (of which 1g saturates), 1g fibre and 0.4g salt.\n', 30, 30, 12, 9),
(360, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/sausage_and_bacon_rustic_54743\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/sausage_and_bacon_rustic_54743_16x9.jpg\n', 'Sausage and bacon rustic hotpot\n', ' Warm up with this homely, comforting bean and sausage hotpot served with melting cheese toasts.\n', 30, 30, 2, 16),
(361, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pot-roast_turkey_75303\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/pot-roast_turkey_75303_16x9.jpg\n', 'Pot-roast turkey drumstick\n', ' Turkey is not just for Christmas! The drumsticks cost very little and stretch a long way - perfect for a meaty pot-roast on a modest budget.\n \n This pot-roast can be cooked in advance and frozen, check the tips section for freezing instructions. \n', 30, 120, 3, 18),
(362, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/crispfriedplaice_90189\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/crispfriedplaice_90189_16x9.jpg\n', 'Crisp fried plaice\n', ' Deep-fry your fish in fizzy batter and eat it hot. \n', 30, 10, 2, 8),
(363, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/quick_chicken_korma_62072\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/quick_chicken_korma_62072_16x9.jpg\n', 'Korma-style chicken curry \n', ' Mary Berry\'s easy chicken korma-style curry is mild enough for all the family to enjoy. Mary replaces the usual cream with yoghurt for a lighter, fresher taste.\n', 30, 30, 4, 19),
(364, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/tuscan_fries_61356\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/tuscan_fries_61356_16x9.jpg\n', 'Tuscan fries\n', ' Cesare Casella, a chef from Lucca, whose family used to run the fabulous Vipore restaurant and who is now cooking in New York, is the man who invented Tuscan fries. Think French fries, but with garlic cloves and fresh herbs thrown into the hot oil towards the end of the cooking time.\n', 30, 30, 4, 7),
(365, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/vietnamese_beef_pho_22510\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/vietnamese_beef_pho_22510_16x9.jpg\n', 'Vietnamese beef pho\n', ' Beef pho is a popular street food from Vietnam, with its delicious combination of fresh ingredients and a spicy, rich stock. \n', 30, 120, 4, 33),
(366, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/banana_blueberry_and_50179\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/banana_blueberry_and_50179_16x9.jpg\n', 'Vegan banana pancakes with blueberries and pecans\n', ' This delicious vegan pancake recipe is made with bananas and oats. A scoop of vegan coconut ice cream will turn them into a feel-good pudding, too.\n', 30, 30, 8, 17),
(367, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/beef_biriyani_96108\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/beef_biriyani_96108_16x9.jpg\n', 'Beef biryani\n', ' This delicious beef biryani is great for freezing – just be sure to allow everything to cool first.\n \n Each serving provides 690 kcal, 46g protein, 56g carbohydrates (of which 11g sugars), 25g fat (of which 8g saturates), 8g fibre and 2.2g salt.\n', 30, 120, 8, 23),
(368, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/panzanella_72070\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/panzanella_72070_16x9.jpg\n', 'Perfect panzanella\n', ' Do not throw away your old bread! Soaking it in a garlicky mixture of red wine vinegar, olive oil and tomato juices will bring it back to life Mediterranean-style for this classic salad. \n', 120, 30, 4, 13),
(369, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/poached_haddock_and_egg_19411\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/poached_haddock_and_egg_19411_16x9.jpg\n', 'Baked poached haddock and egg pots\n', ' These are too good to save for brunch! Serve them with a little salad for a simple and filling meal for two. \n', 30, 30, 2, 11),
(370, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/sweet_and_sour_chicken_52908\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/sweet_and_sour_chicken_52908_16x9.jpg\n', 'Healthy sweet and sour chicken\n', ' This is exactly like your favourite sweet and sour from the local down the road, but with fewer calories. Proves that a diet doesn’t have to be all about denial.\n \n This meal without rice provides 288 kcal, 20g protein, 38g carbohydrate (of which 29g sugars), 7g fat (of which 1g saturates), 3g fibre and 0.1g salt per portion.\n', 30, 10, 4, 18),
(371, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/prune_and_armagnac_tart_36307\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p03c0l0n.jpg\n', 'Prune and Armagnac tart \n', ' Armagnac is a special-occasion tipple, so it’s perfect at Christmas. Try it in this sensational dessert.\n', 90, 90, 8, 15),
(372, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/roast_chicken_with_sage_46297\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/roast_chicken_with_sage_46297_16x9.jpg\n', 'Roast chicken with sage and onion stuffing\n', ' This roast chicken recipe is a real crowd pleaser. The stuffing is a lovely addition that really makes the dish sing. Use our roasting calculator to work out the exact times and temperatures for your roast.\n', NULL, 120, 4, 21),
(373, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chocchippuffypancake_65968\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chocchippuffypancake_65968_16x9.jpg\n', 'Fluffy chocolate chip pancakes\n', ' A sweet treat, these fluffy chocolate chip pancakes are a kid\'s dream, especially as it\'s served with butterscotch ice cream. \n', 30, 10, 2, 10),
(374, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/aubergine_and_mozzarella_51464\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/aubergine_and_mozzarella_51464_16x9.jpg\n', 'Aubergine and mozzarella bake \n', ' A simple vegetarian bake made with mozzarella and aubergine will out-class any lasagne ready-meal. Serve with crusty bread. This is designed to be a low cost recipe.\n', 30, 90, 4, 9),
(375, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/christmas_crumble_88738\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/christmas_crumble_88738_16x9.jpg\n', 'Christmas apple and mincemeat crumble\n', ' This twist on the apple crumble is a great way to use up Christmas marzipan and the jar of mincemeat you have leftover post-Christmas. Let’s get ready to crumble.\n', 30, 90, 6, 16),
(376, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/gammon_with_treacle_81407\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/gammon_with_treacle_81407_16x9.jpg\n', 'Gammon with treacle bacon crust\n', ' It may seem excessive to top a ham with bacon, but Christmas is a time for generosity. \n', 120, 120, 4, 15),
(377, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/moroccanfishstew_84341\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/moroccanfishstew_84341_16x9.jpg\n', 'Moroccan fish stew\n', ' Bill Grainger\'s impressive fish stew with warming spices and chickpeas is fantastically easy to make. Perfect for a relaxed dinner with friends.\n \n Each serving provides 249kcal, 28g protein, 19g carbohydrate (of which 9.5g sugars), 5.5g fat (of which	0.8g saturates), 5g fibre and	0.5g salt.\n', 30, 90, 4, 19),
(378, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/honey-glazed_guinea_fowl_24715\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/honey-glazed_guinea_fowl_24715_16x9.jpg\n', 'Honey-glazed guinea fowl with pomegranate and pineapple\n', ' This recipe is certainly exotic – honey and five-spice chilli guinea fowl served with a fresh fruit salsa splashed with soy sauce. If you can source one, serve in a banana leaf to impress.\n', 30, 90, 4, 16),
(379, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chicken_tagine_with_65235\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chicken_tagine_with_65235_16x9.jpg\n', 'Chicken leg tagine with prunes, apricots and roasted almonds\n', ' The warm flavours of cinnamon, dried fruits and chicken make this tagine a Moroccan classic.\n \n 632 kcal, 50g protein,	46g carbohydrate (of which 44g sugars), 26g fat (of which 4g saturates), 7g fibre and 1.1g salt per portion.\n', 120, 120, 5, 20),
(380, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/roastvegetablesoup_6537\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/roastvegetablesoup_6537_16x9.jpg\n', 'Roast vegetable soup\n', ' This healthy roasted vegetable soup can be made super quickly if you use a bag of frozen roast veg from a supermarket. \n', 30, 90, 2, 9),
