(690, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pennewithtomatoesspi_73926\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/pennewithtomatoesspi_73926_16x9.jpg\n', 'Penne with tomatoes, chorizo and cream\n', ' A simple but impressive pasta dish with the kick of chorizo and crushed chillies balanced by a creamy tomato sauce.\n', 30, 30, 4, 14),
(691, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/cheesy_chorizo_tomato_44387\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/cheesy_chorizo_tomato_44387_16x9.jpg\n', 'Cheesy chorizo, tomato and broccoli pasta bake\n', ' With loads of flavour, this cheesy pasta bake will leave you totally satisfied. By cutting the chorizo into small chunks, you should get a little piece in most mouthfuls so you don’t notice you are eating less meat. This also works for other dishes such as stews, casseroles, curries and pies. \n', 30, 90, 4, 15),
(692, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/spring_lamb_stew_87094\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/spring_lamb_stew_87094_16x9.jpg\n', 'Spring lamb stew\n', ' For the fashion-conscious, the arrival of spring in Paris means that it’s out with the winter wardrobe and in with the spring one. The same goes for stews. Forget your winter boeuf bourguignon, it’s so last season! Navarin d’agneau printanier, a lamb stew with fresh vegetables, is what should be bubbling away in your kitchen.\n', 30, 120, 4, 12),
(693, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/creamy_mushrooms_on_35264\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/creamy_mushrooms_on_35264_16x9.jpg\n', 'Lighter creamy mushrooms on toast \n', ' So creamy and luxurious you\'ll never realise this breakfast is only 200 kcal and counts as one of your five-a-day.\n \n Each serving provides 200 kcal, 17g protein, 14g carbohydrate (of which 3g sugars), 8g fat (of which 3g saturates), 3g fibre and 1.4g salt.\n', 30, 10, 1, 12),
(694, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/grilledteriakichicke_80048\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/grilledteriakichicke_80048_16x9.jpg\n', 'Teriyaki chicken with leek and pepper stir-fry\n', ' Chicken thighs are more flavourful than breasts and a lot cheaper, perfect if you\'re solo cooking on a budget. \n \n Each serving provides 404kcal, 23g protein, 20g carbohydrate (of which 20g sugars), 25g fat (of which 4g saturates), 2.6g fibre and	2.3g salt.\n', 30, 10, 1, 8),
(695, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/lentils_and_goats_cheese_09590\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/lentils_and_goats_cheese_09590_16x9.jpg\n', 'Lentil and goats\' cheese salad\n', ' This combination of earthy lentils, tangy goats\' cheese and fragrant basil is really satisfying. Serve it with salad leaves and crusty bread.\n \n Each serving provides 288 kcal, 20.5g protein, 24.5g carbohydrates (of which 1g sugars), 11g fat (of which 7g saturates), 6g fibre and 0.6g salt. \n', 30, 30, 2, 8),
(696, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/marinated_minty_lamb_61532\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/marinated_minty_lamb_61532_16x9.jpg\n', 'Marinated minty lamb kebabs\n', ' Lamb and mint is a classic combination. Cook on skewers with pepper and onion to add crunch and serve with couscous for a healthy evening meal.\n \n This meal is low calorie and provides 421 kcal, 27g protein, 57g carbohydrate (of which 7.5g sugars), 9g fat (of which 3.5g saturates), 1.5g fibre and 0.3g salt per portion.\n', 30, 30, 4, 12),
(697, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/raspberry_and_white_81250\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/raspberry_and_white_81250_16x9.jpg\n', 'Raspberry and white chocolate pavlova\n', ' This raspberry and white chocolate pavlova makes a spectacular dessert. It\'s ideal for special occasions because it can all be made well ahead.\n \n For this recipe, you will need an electric mixer, one large baking tray and a cooking thermometer.\n \n \n', 120, 120, 16, 15),
(698, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mincemeat_and_orange_21941\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mincemeat_and_orange_21941_16x9.jpg\n', 'Mary Berry\'s mince pies\n', ' Mary Berry\'s mince pies will win any Christmas get-together. These Christmassy bites have delicious orangey pastry and grated marzipan on top that gives a wonderful flavour.\n \n Equipment and preparation: for this recipe you will need a 12-hole muffin tin and 8cm/3in fluted pastry cutter. \n \n \n', 30, 30, 12, 8),
(699, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/courgette_and_mint_16928\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/courgette_and_mint_16928_16x9.jpg\n', 'Courgette and mint frittata\n', ' Frittatas are perfect for a quick brunch or light lunch. Add some courgette and mint for extra flavour and to help you get your five a day. \n \n This meal is low calorie and provides 256 kcal, 13g protein, 3.5g carbohydrate (of which 3g sugars), 21.4g fat (of which 4.3g saturates), 1.6g fibre and 0.3g salt per portion.\n', 30, 30, 4, 7),
(700, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/southern-fried_97953\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/southern-fried_97953_16x9.jpg\n', 'Southern-fried buttermilk chicken with tomato salsa\n', ' This fried chicken is proper Saturday-night dinner territory - serve it on a giant sharing plate so all the family can dive in.\n', NULL, 30, 4, 22),
(701, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/easter_simnel_cake_82449\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/easter_simnel_cake_82449_16x9.jpg\n', 'Easter simnel cake\n', ' Simnel cake was traditionally given by servant girls to their mothers when they returned home on Mothering Sunday. But it\'s now become a classic Easter cake.\n', 30, 120, 10, 12),
(702, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/keralan_kozhi_kuttan_64529\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/keralan_kozhi_kuttan_64529_16x9.jpg\n', 'Keralan chicken curry\n', ' A creamy South Indian coconut chicken curry recipe that\'s packed with flavour and served with zingy rice for freshness. \n', 120, 90, 4, 38),
(703, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/posh_fish_and_chips_96392\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/posh_fish_and_chips_96392_16x9.jpg\n', 'Gremolata fish with tartare sauce\n', ' Keep a careful eye on the gremolata crumb as you grill the fish for this posh fish and chips to get the topping to just the right crispness.\n \n Each serving provides 517 kcal, 41g protein, 53g carbohydrates (of which 5g sugars), 14g fat (of which 2g saturates), 7g fibre and 1.4g salt.\n', 30, 90, 4, 19),
(704, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/panforte_54621\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/panforte_54621_16x9.jpg\n', 'Panforte\n', ' This Italian speciality is perfect for homemade gifts or for finishing a festive meal, simply served with dessert wine or coffee. \n', 30, 120, 20, 20),
(705, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/paul_hollywoods_scones_70005\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/paul_hollywoods_scones_70005_16x9.jpg\n', 'Paul Hollywood\'s scones\n', ' A simple recipe for soft and fluffy scones that are perfect with jam and plenty of clotted cream. \n', 30, 30, 8, 13),
(706, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/fondant_fancies_88368\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/fondant_fancies_88368_16x9.jpg\n', 'Mary Berry\'s fondant fancies\n', ' Surprise your friends (and indeed yourself) with a batch of these homemade fondant fancies. Plus there’s plenty of fun to be had choosing your own colours and flavours.\n \n Equipment and Preparation: You will need a piping bag, free-standing mixer and a 20cm/8in square tin.\n', 90, 90, 25, 15),
(707, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/curried_cauliflower_soup_51373\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/curried_cauliflower_soup_51373_16x9.jpg\n', 'Curried cauliflower soup\n', ' This smooth, creamy cauliflower soup is a soothing and luxurious winter dish that can easily be jazzed up for guests.\n', 30, 30, 4, 14),
(708, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/goat_tagine_with_toasted_74021\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p03dpww8.jpg\n', 'Goat tagine with toasted nut couscous\n', ' This fragrant goat tagine is packed with dried fruit, nuts and fresh herbs and can be on the table in just over an hour.\n', 90, 120, 4, 37),
(709, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/bouillabaisse_00342\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/bouillabaisse_00342_16x9.jpg\n', 'Bouillabaisse \n', ' Bouillabaisse was originally a stew made by Marseille fishermen using the bony rockfish which they were unable to sell to restaurants or markets. Now it\'s made from any type of fish that\'s available. Look out for sustainable fish when shopping.\n', 30, 30, 6, 27),
(710, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/potato_tart_with_mustard_36933\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p0105r5f.jpg\n', 'Potato tart with mustard, leeks and mushrooms\n', ' Potato pastry is a wonderful way of using up leftover mashed potato, and this savoury tart is delicious hot or cold.\n', 90, 90, 4, 20),
(711, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/fettucine_bolognese_with_17680\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/fettucine_bolognese_with_17680_16x9.jpg\n', 'Fettuccine Bolognese with pangrattato \n', ' Smarten-up your spag bol with an easy pangrattato topping – it might sound fancy but it\'s just fried breadcrumbs flavoured with rosemary and garlic. Ideal for a low-key dinner party.\n', 30, 120, 4, 25),
(712, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/honey_mustard_and_garlic_02558\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/honey_mustard_and_garlic_02558_16x9.jpg\n', 'Honey mustard chicken with sweet potato mash\n', ' Spatchcocked chicken takes far less cooking time than a regular roast, so this honey mustard chicken can be ready in no time.\n', 30, 90, 4, 20),
(713, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/slow_cooker_chipotle_23720\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/slow_cooker_chipotle_23720_16x9.jpg\n', 'Slow cooker pulled pork\n', ' This slow cooker pulled pork recipe is great for feeding a crowd. It\'s so easy people won\'t believe how little effort it takes. Get a really good chipotle sauce if you want a bit of heat. \n', 30, 120, 4, 15);
INSERT INTO `recipe_info` (`recipe_id`, `recipe_url`, `image_url`, `title`, `description`, `preparation_time`, `cook_time`, `serving_count`, `ingredient_count`) VALUES
(714, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/soy-glazed_salmon_salad_50598\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/soy-glazed_salmon_salad_50598_16x9.jpg\n', 'Soy-glazed salmon salad\n', ' The combination of bright crunchy vegetables brings both colour and flavour to this light and fresh-tasting salmon salad.\n \n Each serving provides 320 kcal, 27g protein, 9g carbohydrates (of which 8g sugars), 19g fat (of which 3.5g saturates), 4g fibre and 2g salt.\n', 120, 30, 4, 20),
(715, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/horseradish_and_mustard_10990\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/horseradish_and_mustard_10990_16x9.jpg\n', 'Beef casserole with horseradish and mustard\n', ' Mary Berry\'s hearty, slow-cooked beef casserole is perfect for the Christmas holidays. Serve with mash and seasonal veg.\n', 30, 120, 6, 16),
(716, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chocolate_macaroons_19613\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chocolate_macaroons_19613_16x9.jpg\n', 'Chocolate macaroons\n', ' Raymond Blanc reveals the secrets to the perfect macaroon, one of the benchmarks by which a good patisserie is measured. You may need a little practice to get them right but, as M Blanc says, “every mistake will still be delicious. Trust me; I know!” \n \n Equipment and preparation: You will need a kitchen mixer, a sugar thermometer and a piping bag fitted with an 8mm/¼in nozzle.\n', 90, 30, 30, 12),
(717, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/crunchypeanutbutterc_87012\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/crunchypeanutbutterc_87012_16x9.jpg\n', 'Peanut butter cookies\n', ' Paul Rankin\'s easy recipe for peanut butter cookies takes only 15 minutes to make. You could whip up a batch after school and eat them warm.\n', 30, 10, 8, 6),
(718, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/tortapasquale_88435\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/tortapasquale_88435_16x9.jpg\n', 'Easter spinach pie (torta pasquale)\n', ' A beautiful vegetarian Easter feast, this authentic Italian pie is stuffed with fresh greens and rich eggs and is perfect for eating throughout the summer.\n', 30, 90, 6, 26),
(719, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/barbecue_chicken_and_82515\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/barbecue_chicken_and_82515_16x9.jpg\n', 'Barbecue chicken and rice wraps\n', ' Make your own quick barbecue spice mix for these easy barbecue-style chicken and rice wraps and save a packet on, er, packets. Part  of Rob\'s chicken meal prep series, also check out his speedy chicken couscous and chicken cashew curry for the full set. \n', 30, 30, 2, 20),
(720, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/fish_tacos_33979\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/fish_tacos_33979_16x9.jpg\n', 'Fish tacos\n', ' These fish tacos are excellent, and rest assured that the actual preparation is much easier than you might think. \n', 30, 30, 4, 24),
(721, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chicken_egg_fried_rice_50450\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chicken_egg_fried_rice_50450_16x9.jpg\n', 'Chicken egg-fried rice\n', ' Chicken egg-fried rice is a quick, easy and cheap way to use up leftovers. Perfect for late-night meals or dinner in a hurry.\n \n Each serving provides 702 kcal, 4g protein, 79g carbohydrates (of which 11g sugars), 24g fat (of which 5g saturates), 6g fibre and 3.5g salt.\n', 30, 10, 1, 8),
(722, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/leekrisottowithparme_92285\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/leekrisottowithparme_92285_16x9.jpg\n', 'Leek risotto with parmesan crisps\n', ' Use the chicken stock from a Sunday roast to give beautiful flavour to this comforting leek risotto.\n', 30, 90, 2, 9),
(723, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/breakfast_bars_20_09760\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/breakfast_bars_20_09760_16x9.jpg\n', 'Breakfast bars 2.0\n', ' This is my new, improved breakfast bar recipe: gluten-free, dairy-free and enough seeds to make you start sprouting. I’ve used no sugar, but before you start thinking this is virtuously sugar-free (which I could claim it to be), remember that the sweetness that comes from the dates is, in essence, sugar, though certainly it’s unprocessed and full of fibre at the same time.\n \n Make these bars at the weekend, and you’ll be set up for the week if you’re someone who needs to grab-and-go in the morning. \n', 30, 30, 16, 9),
(724, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/one-pot_chicken_with_55660\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/one-pot_chicken_with_55660_16x9.jpg\n', 'One-pot chicken with dates and caramelised lemon\n', ' This makes a great alternative Sunday lunch when you fancy a roast but want something a bit different. \n', 30, 120, 4, 29),
(725, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/snow_man_biscuits_33998\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/snow_man_biscuits_33998_16x9.jpg\n', 'Snowman Christmas cookies\n', ' Follow our step-by-step guide to making these cute snowman Christmas cookies. A great treat for kids to make or just to eat.\n', 90, 30, 24, 11),
(726, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/lamb_and_vegetable_30192\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/lamb_and_vegetable_30192_16x9.jpg\n', 'Lamb tagine with chickpeas\n', ' Take your time to make this tender, slow-cooked lamb tagine recipe packed with vegetables and healthy chickpeas. A family favourite!\n', 30, 120, 6, 22),
(727, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/asparagus_with_pearl_43154\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/asparagus_with_pearl_43154_16x9.jpg\n', 'Asparagus with pearl barley and bacon\n', ' Hearty and nutritious barley is given a makeover in this creamy springtime supper.\n', 30, 90, 4, 16),
(728, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mini_victoria_sponge_61310\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mini_victoria_sponge_61310_16x9.jpg\n', 'Mini Victoria sponge cakes\n', ' We’ve zapped the classic Mary Berry Victoria sponge with a shrink ray to make these adorable little cakes.\n \n Equipment and preparation: for this recipe you will need a 12-cup mini sandwich tin and a piping bag fitted with a 1cm/½in plain nozzle\n', 30, 30, 12, 10),
(729, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/perfect_apple_pie_73735\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/perfect_apple_pie_73735_16x9.jpg\n', 'Perfect apple pie\n', ' Perfect your pastry to the Hairy Bikers’ standard with this delicious Bramley apple pie recipe. A deep pie dish is essential for fitting in as many hot, fluffy apples as you can. Serve with vanilla ice cream.\n', 30, 90, 6, 11),
(730, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/potato_bread_39335\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/potato_bread_39335_16x9.jpg\n', 'Potato bread (Kartoffelbrot)\n', ' This is a deliciously moist, soft bread, which is perfect with white asparagus soup. It really is a multi-purpose bread and great for sandwiches or fried.\n', 120, 90, 1, 10),
(731, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/lemon_drizzle_traybake_01890\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/lemon_drizzle_traybake_01890_16x9.jpg\n', 'Lemon drizzle traybake\n', ' Mary Berry\'s lemon drizzle traybake cake has been a hit since the 1960s, and this is the recipe she is most asked for when stopped in the street.\n \n Equipment and preparation: for this recipe you will need a 30x23cm/12x9in tray bake or roasting tin.\n \n \n \n Each serving provides 290 kcal, 4g protein, 38.5g carbohydrates (of which 25g sugars), 13.5g fat (of which 8g saturates), 0.7g fibre and 0.6g salt.\n', 30, 90, 16, 10),
(732, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mintedfetarocketando_67597\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mintedfetarocketando_67597_16x9.jpg\n', 'Healthy pasta salad\n', ' Our healthy pasta salad, bursting with herby goodness can be made in a matter of minutes.\n \n This meal, if served as eight portions, provides 260kcal, 11g protein, 34g carbohydrate (of which 2g sugars), 8g fat (of which 4g saturates), 3.5g fibre and 0.9g salt per portion.\n', 30, 30, 6, 13),
(733, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/lambpepperandpineapp_91704\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/lambpepperandpineapp_91704_16x9.jpg\n', 'Lamb, pepper and pineapple kebabs with lime, chilli and coriander mayonnaise\n', ' Try a pineapple marinade on cheaper cuts of meat - and let the enzymes work their magic for sweet, tender barbecue food with a Jamaican feel.\n', 120, 30, 10, 26),
(734, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/definitivechocolatec_72226\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/definitivechocolatec_72226_16x9.jpg\n', 'Mary\'s chocolate cake\n', ' Chocolate cake meets Victoria sponge in Mary\'s easiest ever chocolate cake recipe filled with cream and jam. \n', 30, 90, 8, 8),
(735, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chickpea_date_and_cashew_81632\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chickpea_date_and_cashew_81632_16x9.jpg\n', 'Chickpea, date and cashew bites\n', ' You would never know that chickpeas form the base of these protein-packed no-bake energy squares. The toasted nuts, dates and chocolate make this taste like an indulgent treat.\n \n \n \n Watch the video for three easy no-bake snack ideas. Get the chocolate and date raw brownie recipe here or find the peanut and coconut energy balls recipe here.\n', 30, NULL, 24, 7),
(736, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/savoury_pies_with_14115\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/savoury_pies_with_14115_16x9.jpg\n', 'Savoury pies with Jarlsberg cheese and ham (Norwegian pierogi)\n', ' Every country has something like these little pies – Polish pierogi, Indian samosas, Spanish and Argentinian empanadas – and this is Norway\'s version, made with Jarlsberg cheese and caraway seeds for that special Norwegian flavour. We give these dix points! If you\'re a lazybones you could use puff pastry, but you\'ll end up with something that\'s more like a fried pasty. Try these as a great little starter or beer blotter.\n', 120, 30, 12, 20),
(737, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chickentagine_74834\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chickentagine_74834_16x9.jpg\n', 'Chicken tagine\n', ' A tasty, aromatic chicken tagine recipe. Serve with couscous for a filling supper.\n', 30, 90, 4, 14),
(738, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/okra_curry_68708\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/okra_curry_68708_16x9.jpg\n', 'Okra curry\n', ' A quick vegan and vegetarian okra curry that works just as well as a side dish. It\'s important to wash and dry the okra before chopping them, or they will become slimey. \n', 30, 30, 4, 10),
(739, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/bangbangchicken_82544\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/bangbangchicken_82544_16x9.jpg\n', 'Bang bang chicken\n', ' A vibrant chicken recipe full of bold flavours from chilli, peanut and lime. Use leftover roast chicken, if you like.\n', 30, 10, 2, 26),
(740, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/roast_turkey_crown_10545\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/roast_turkey_crown_10545_16x9.jpg\n', 'Stuffed roast turkey breast \n', ' Less than 2 hours of roasting makes this roast turkey breast a relatively quick Christmas dinner. As well as lemon and thyme, the stuffing features tart dried cranberries, crunchy almonds and sweet leeks.\n', 90, 120, 8, 21),
