(793, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/beef_chilli_con_carne_92275\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/beef_chilli_con_carne_92275_16x9.jpg\n', 'How to make chilli con carne\n', ' Chilli con carne is an all-time favourite party dish that’s incredibly easy to make, served here with a little grated chocolate for a bit of Mexican authenticity. Make your chilli in advance for even better flavour.\n', 30, 120, 4, 23),
(794, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/griddle_pan_pumpkin_16498\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/griddle_pan_pumpkin_16498_16x9.jpg\n', 'Griddle pan pumpkin waffles\n', ' Make brunch seasonal by adding pumpkin or squash to your waffles. No waffle iron? No problem! These are made in a griddle pan.\n \n We used a 26x26cm/10x10in griddle pan, if you use a larger pan the mixture will make fewer waffles. \n', 30, 90, 4, 11),
(795, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/fettuccine_alfredo_47554\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/fettuccine_alfredo_47554_16x9.jpg\n', 'Fettuccine Alfredo\n', ' It doesn’t get much easier (or creamier) than this fettucine alfredo, ready in the time it takes to cook the pasta.\n', 30, 30, 4, 6),
(796, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/garlic_and_parmesan_mash_80742\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/garlic_and_parmesan_mash_80742_16x9.jpg\n', 'Garlic and Parmesan mash\n', ' I’m not, as a rule, one for flavouring mashed potatoes, but this version is a worthy exception. Because the garlic cloves are boiled with the potatoes, they make their presence felt sweetly rather than shoutily, and the Parmesan provides a gentle tang. \n', 30, 90, 6, 12),
(797, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/velodrome_cake_45072\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/velodrome_cake_45072_16x9.jpg\n', 'Velodrome cake\n', ' Take gold in cake-baking with this stunning re-creation of the velodrome in cake - cycling fans will be delighted. \n', 30, 90, 12, 8),
(798, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/berry_yoghurt_95274\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/berry_yoghurt_95274_16x9.jpg\n', 'Berry yoghurt\n', ' A luscious, fruity yogurt that makes a satisfying breakfast. Using frozen berries saves money and they make a delicious juice as they thaw. \n \n As part of an Intermittent diet plan, 1 serving provides:\n \n Your daily piece of fruit\n \n 2 of your 3 daily low-fat dairy portions\n \n This meal provides 149 kcal per portion.\n', 30, NULL, 2, 3),
(799, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/coconut_chicken_50197\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/coconut_chicken_50197_16x9.jpg\n', 'Coconut chicken\n', ' These coconut chicken goujons from Eat Well for Less are easy and affordable. It\'s the perfect finger food for parties or even as an after-school snack.\n \n Each serving provides 429 kcal, 35g protein, 15g carbohydrate (of which 3g sugars), 25g fat (of which 11g saturates), 3g fibre and 0.8g salt.\n', 30, 30, 2, 11),
(800, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chicken_casserole_49479\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chicken_casserole_49479_16x9.jpg\n', 'Italian chicken casserole\n', ' The list of recipes for a chicken casserole is quite numerous: with or without tomatoes, onions, herbs and so on. But the thing that really matters is to get a good chicken. This is one of my favourite ways to do it. \n', 30, 120, 4, 15),
(801, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/ruby-red_plum_and_83013\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/ruby-red_plum_and_83013_16x9.jpg\n', 'Ruby-red plum and amaretti crumble\n', ' Along with a lot of not traditionally Italian baking, the good old English crumble has seemed to be gaining popularity – even modishness – in Italy. By all means, use other-coloured plums – or indeed any other fruit you feel like – but be prepared to modify lemon and sugar content accordingly.\n', 30, 90, 4, 10),
(802, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/seabassfilletwithros_72151\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/seabassfilletwithros_72151_16x9.jpg\n', 'Sea bass fillet with rosemary and lemon\n', ' A simple and delicious sea bass recipe for one. Wonderful served with mashed or roasted sweet potato. \n', 30, 10, 1, 5),
(803, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/crabsalmonanddillfis_93618\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/crabsalmonanddillfis_93618_16x9.jpg\n', 'Crab and salmon fishcakes with homemade tartare sauce\n', ' Prepare the fishcakes in advance and chill. Remove from the fridge 30 minutes before cooking, and fry just before serving.\n', 90, 90, 2, 28),
(804, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/roast_chicken_02598\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p02ffwgt.jpg\n', 'Roast chicken\n', ' Try this classic roast chicken recipe with a fricassée of spring vegetables for a fresh, no-fuss Sunday lunch.\n', 30, 120, 4, 11),
(805, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/roasted_butternut_squash_10281\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/roasted_butternut_squash_10281_16x9.jpg\n', 'Mary Berry\'s butternut squash soup\n', ' This easy butternut squash soup recipe is completely dairy-free! It has added red pepper and ginger, and is deliciously smooth. \n \n For this recipe you will need a 3.5–4 litre/6–7 pint deep-sided saucepan. \n', 30, 90, 8, 14),
(806, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/warm_spiced_oranges_with_20973\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/warm_spiced_oranges_with_20973_16x9.jpg\n', 'Warm, spiced oranges with labneh\n', ' Labneh is a thick strained yoghurt that is easy to make using natural yoghurt. Topped with warm spiced oranges it makes a wonderful breakfast or light dessert. \n \n With a GI of 39 this meal is high protein, low GI and  provides 193 kcal per portion. \n \n \n', NULL, 10, 2, 6),
(807, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/carrot_and_sultana_cake_49411\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/carrot_and_sultana_cake_49411_16x9.jpg\n', 'Carrot and sultana cake with creamy orange frosting\n', ' A luxurious tasting carrot cake packed with sultanas and pecans. One piece is never enough.\n', 30, 90, 12, 19),
(808, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/instantbananaicecrea_86115\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/instantbananaicecrea_86115_16x9.jpg\n', 'Instant banana ice cream\n', ' An easy instant banana ice cream recipe that all the family will love. Instantly. Top with berries, dark chocolate drops or whatever you fancy.\n', 90, NULL, 4, 1),
(809, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/noodlesaladwithchill_85919\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/noodlesaladwithchill_85919_16x9.jpg\n', 'Noodle salad with chilli nuts\n', ' Salad is not just about lettuce, this zingy noodle salad is perfect for popping in your lunchbox. \n', 30, 10, 1, 12),
(810, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/smokey_mutton_sloppy_joe_19958\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/smokey_mutton_sloppy_joe_19958_16x9.jpg\n', 'Smoky mutton Sloppy Joe with crispy lamb’s breast\n', ' Impress your friends with these tasty lamb Sloppy Joe’s, perfect for a party. If you don\'t have time to make the crispy lamb\'s breast garnish you can substitute with crisps. \n', NULL, 120, 4, 24),
(811, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/loin_of_pork_with_00990\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/loin_of_pork_with_00990_16x9.jpg\n', 'Pork loin with scrumpy sauce, candied walnuts and cabbage\n', ' Pork chops aren\'t just for midweek meals - this recipe shows you how to turn them into something really special. \n', 30, 90, 4, 20),
(812, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/roast_rib_of_beef_bone_98290\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/roast_rib_of_beef_bone_98290_16x9.jpg\n', 'Roast rib of beef and bone marrow gravy with roast potatoes \n', ' Rib of beef makes a show stopping roast. Especially when you add bone marrow gravy. \n', 30, 120, 6, 25),
(813, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/veggie_sausage_tray_bake_99019\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/veggie_sausage_tray_bake_99019_16x9.jpg\n', 'Veggie sausage tray bake \n', ' Homemade vegan sausages may take a little longer to make than shop-bought, but you\'ll be so glad you made the effort.\n \n Each serving provides 541 kcal, 18g protein, 44g carbohydrates (of which 18g sugars), 29g fat (of which 3.5g saturates), 16g fibre and 1.7g salt.\n', 30, 30, 2, 26),
(814, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/cheesesauce_1299\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/cheesesauce_1299_16x9.jpg\n', 'Cheese sauce\n', ' Learn how to make cheese sauce with this easy recipe. Great for cauliflower cheese, fish pies and pasta.\n \n Each serving provides 216 kcal, 9g protein, 9g carbohydrates (of which 4.5g sugars), 16g fat (of which 10g saturates), 0g fibre and 0.8g salt.\n', 30, 30, 4, 6),
(815, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/toastedcashewandchil_89382\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/toastedcashewandchil_89382_16x9.jpg\n', 'Toasted cashew and chilli broccoli salad with sesame soy dressing\n', ' Make sure your salad packs a crunch with broccoli florets and tasty cashews. \n', 30, 10, 1, 5),
(816, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/bras_de_gitan_63262\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/bras_de_gitan_63262_16x9.jpg\n', 'Bras de gitan\n', ' Gypsy’s arm. This posh Swiss roll is made with ground almonds and a splash of liqueur and filled with delicious crème pat.\n', 120, 30, 8, 22),
(817, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mushroom_doner_22676\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mushroom_doner_22676_16x9.jpg\n', 'Mushroom doner\n', ' A meat-free mushroom ‘doner’ kebab packed with two types of sauces, pickles and veg. A mighty delicious vegetarian dish. \n', 30, 30, 4, 22),
(818, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chickpea_burgers_00951\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chickpea_burgers_00951_16x9.jpg\n', 'Vegan burgers\n', ' These delicious vegan burgers are quick and easy to make. They can be prepared in advance and left in the fridge until you\'re ready to cook.\n', 30, 30, 4, 24),
(819, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/sticky_toffee_pudding_50947\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/sticky_toffee_pudding_50947_16x9.jpg\n', 'Sticky toffee pudding\n', ' A recipe for sticky toffee pudding is sacred in the kitchen of a discerning cook. \n', 30, 90, 4, 17),
(820, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chicken_and_chorizo_rice_85780\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chicken_and_chorizo_rice_85780_16x9.jpg\n', 'Chicken and chorizo rice\n', ' Save on effort and washing up with this one-pot wonder that is packed with flavour. Eat some for dinner and save the rest for lunch the next day. \n', 30, 30, 2, 11),
(821, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/baby_aubergines_with_49593\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/baby_aubergines_with_49593_16x9.jpg\n', 'Baby aubergines with oregano and red onions\n', ' I like the way this dish can be eaten as a starter or part of an antipasti table, and even more as a main course, sprinkled with some ricotta salata (the deliciously salted, dried kind) or crumbled feta, or as an accompaniment to meat and fish.\n \n Each serving provides 140kcal, 1g protein, 3g carbohydrate (of which 3g sugars), 13g fat (of which 2g saturates), 2.5g fibre and 0.8g salt.\n', 30, 90, 6, 11),
(822, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chewy_lemon_and_thyme_92523\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chewy_lemon_and_thyme_92523_16x9.jpg\n', 'Chewy lemon and thyme cookies\n', ' These dairy-free, flourless cookies are perfect for vegans and those following a gluten-free diet.\n \n Each cookie provides 108 kcal, 3g protein, 5g carbohydrate (of which 3g sugars), 8.5g fat (of which 0.7g saturates), 0.5g fibre and 0.2g salt.\n', 30, 30, 10, 8),
(823, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/cheesycauliflowerand_85829\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/cheesycauliflowerand_85829_16x9.jpg\n', 'Cauliflower cheese soup\n', ' Like soup? Love cauliflower cheese? This recipe is for you! Accompanied by irresistible cheesy, crunchy croûtons.\n', 30, 90, 4, 22),
(824, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/sprucedupvanillacake_90703\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/sprucedupvanillacake_90703_16x9.jpg\n', 'Spruced-up vanilla cake\n', ' Nigella\'s simple vanilla cake is anything but boring. Perfect as a Christmas dessert or with a cup of tea as an afternoon treat.\n', 30, 90, 12, 8),
(825, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/yule_log_15656\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/yule_log_15656_16x9.jpg\n', 'Mary Berry\'s yule log\n', ' Mary Berry shows you how to make a foolproof chocolate yule log a.k.a Bûche de Noël. It\'s utterly delicious and a perfect alternative to Christmas pudding! \n', 30, 30, 8, 10),
(826, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/fairycakes_83889\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/fairycakes_83889_16x9.jpg\n', 'Chocolate fairy cakes\n', ' Cute as buttons and tasty too, these fairy cakes are children-friendly: easy, light on washing up and made in minutes.\n', 30, 30, 24, 10),
(827, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/strawberry_and_banana_24556\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/strawberry_and_banana_24556_16x9.jpg\n', 'Sugar-free strawberry and banana ice cream \n', ' This tasty ice-cream contains no added sugar, getting its sweetness from strawberries and vanilla. \n \n Equipment and preparation: for this recipe you will need a pre-chilled ice cream maker. \n \n \n \n This ice-cream without the topping contains 285 kcal, 4.5g protein, 9g carbohydrate (of which 8g sugars), 26g fat (of which 14.5g saturates), 1g fibre and 0g salt per portion. \n', 120, 10, 8, 6),
(828, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/tortelliniwithspinac_82375\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/tortelliniwithspinac_82375_16x9.jpg\n', 'Tortellini with spinach and ricotta\n', ' This classic spinach and ricotta fresh tortellini made by grandmothers all over Italy - it\'s a labour of love, but worth it.\n', 30, 10, 4, 15),
(829, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/breakfast_trifle_28628\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p07hsnwg.jpg\n', 'Chia, yoghurt and granola trifle\n', ' Made with yoghurt, chia seeds, brioche, summer fruits and granola, this is a lighter version of the classic dessert.\n', 30, NULL, 6, 10),
(830, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mary_berrys_easter_46791\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mary_berrys_easter_46791_16x9.jpg\n', 'Mary Berry’s Easter biscuits\n', ' These buttery lemon biscuits are easy to make and take very little time. \n', 30, 30, 24, 7),
(831, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/easy_pizza_with_parma_02334\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/easy_pizza_with_parma_02334_16x9.jpg\n', 'Easy tortilla pizza with Parma ham\n', ' What a brilliant idea – baking tortillas to use as pizza bases. A quick and easy supper on the table in less than half an hour. Result.\n \n Each serving provides 440 kcal, 28g protein, 41g carbohydrates (of which 9g sugars), 19.5g fat (of which 7g saturates), 8g fibre and 3.4g salt.\n', 30, 30, 2, 20),
(832, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/cupcakes_99366\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/cupcakes_99366_16x9.jpg\n', 'Vanilla cupcake\n', ' Follow our simple step-by-step vanilla cupcake srecipe and video. Dan Lepard shows how to make next-level cupcakes with silky buttercream.\n', 30, 120, 12, 24),
(833, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/tamarind_prawns_with_36430\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/tamarind_prawns_with_36430_16x9.jpg\n', 'Tamarind prawns with mushrooms, pak choi and bulgur wheat\n', ' Hot, sweet-and-sour tamarind prawns work beautifully with mushrooms and pak choi in this easy traybake.\n \n Each serving provides 350 kcal, 26.4g protein, 53g carbohydrates (of which 16g sugars), 2g fat (of which 0.5g saturates), 7.5g fibre and 0.7g salt. \n', 30, 30, 2, 11),
(834, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/roastedvegetablelasa_77405\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/roastedvegetablelasa_77405_16x9.jpg\n', 'Roasted vegetable lasagne\n', ' This hearty vegetable lasagne will be loved by vegetarians and meat-eaters alike. Serve with a green salad and crusty bread.\n', 30, 90, 4, 13),
(835, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/slow-cooker_lamb_and_79282\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/slow-cooker_lamb_and_79282_16x9.jpg\n', 'Slow cooker lamb and sweet potato tagine\n', ' Lamb tagine is a classic and this slow cooker recipe uses the best of Moroccan ingredients.\n \n \n \n Each serving provides 532 kcal, 33g protein, 65g carbohydrates (of which 21g sugars), 13g fat (of which 4.5g saturates), 12g fibre and 2g salt.\n \n \n \n \n', 30, 120, 6, 34);
INSERT INTO `recipe_info` (`recipe_id`, `recipe_url`, `image_url`, `title`, `description`, `preparation_time`, `cook_time`, `serving_count`, `ingredient_count`) VALUES
(836, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/somersetchicken_91978\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/somersetchicken_91978_16x9.jpg\n', 'Somerset chicken\n', ' Creamy chicken with a taste of the South West: apples and cider. This is comfort food at its finest. \n', 30, 90, 6, 17),
(837, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/portuguesecustardtar_91040\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/portuguesecustardtar_91040_16x9.jpg\n', 'Portuguese custard tarts\n', ' These little beauties are easier and quicker than a trip to the bakery. They\'re almost too easy.\n', 30, 30, 12, 10),
(838, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/tuna_and_broccoli_pasta_25783\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/tuna_and_broccoli_pasta_25783_16x9.jpg\n', 'Tuna and broccoli pasta bake\n', ' Raid your store cupboard to make a healthy tuna pasta bake in a hurry. Finishing the pasta bake under the grill saves time, too.\n', 30, 30, 4, 12),
(839, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mustard_and_lemon_49577\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mustard_and_lemon_49577_16x9.jpg\n', 'Mustard and lemon sausages with carrot mash\n', ' Nigel Slater’s version of bangers and mash is quick, easy and full of flavour. Try it today and taste the difference.\n', 30, 90, 4, 7),
(840, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/sweet_potato_and_68565\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/sweet_potato_and_68565_16x9.jpg\n', 'Sweet potato and chickpea curry \n', ' This easy sweet potato and chickpea curry takes only a few store cupboard staples - perfect for a laid-back supper. This is designed to be a low cost recipe.\n \n Each serving provides 551kcal, 15.5g protein, 97g carbohydrate (of which 14.5g sugars),	8g fat (of which 1g saturates), 13g fibre and 0.2g salt.\n \n \n', 30, 30, 4, 14),
(841, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/panfriedratatouille_9975\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/panfriedratatouille_9975_16x9.jpg\n', 'Pan-fried ratatouille\n', ' Serve up this tried-and-tested ratatouile recipe - a perfect taste of Provence.\n', 30, 30, 4, 14),
(842, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/roasted_sausage_and_39127\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/roasted_sausage_and_39127_16x9.jpg\n', 'Roasted sausage and potato supper\n', ' This will become a firm family favourite as it can be cooked in one dish and is so quick and easy to put together. Choose your favourite type of local, British sausage for this recipe – my family loves leek and sage.\n', 30, 90, 4, 11),
(843, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/gemelli_with_anchovies_80715\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/gemelli_with_anchovies_80715_16x9.jpg\n', 'Gemelli with anchovies, tomatoes and mascarpone\n', ' Quick, simple and – much as I hate the word – tasty. I know no self-respecting Italian would let tomato seeds sully a sauce, but I do so very happily, and it’s the gloop inside the halved cherry tomatoes that adds cohesion to the spicy, tangy creaminess. \n', 30, 30, 2, 11),
(844, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/quick_orange_and_lemon_60372\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/quick_orange_and_lemon_60372_16x9.jpg\n', 'Quick Chinese citrus chicken stir-fry\n', ' Orange and lemon zest give a zingy flavour to this chicken stir fry, served with garlicky Chinese greens and rice.\n', 30, 30, 4, 18),
