(1126, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/last_minute_christmas_08523\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/last_minute_christmas_08523_16x9.jpg\n', 'Last minute Christmas chutney\n', ' Liven up your buffet table and use up any dried fruit left over from your Christmas baking in this instant chutney.\n', 30, 90, 1, 14),
