(1146, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mushroom_stroganoff_80260\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mushroom_stroganoff_80260_16x9.jpg\n', 'Mushroom stroganoff\n', ' Try this quick, creamy and comforting vegetarian casserole with brown or basmati rice.\n', 30, 30, 4, 13),
