(1405, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/quinoa_and_halloumi_57964\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/quinoa_and_halloumi_57964_16x9.jpg\n', 'Quinoa and halloumi burger\n', ' These tasty vegetarian halloumi burgers use quinoa for a healthier alternative to meat or takeaways. They\'re gluten-free too. \n \n Each burger provides 122 kcal, 6.5g protein, 11g carbohydrate (of which 1.3g sugars), 6g fat (of which 3.5g saturates), 0.5g fibre and 0.5g salt. \n', NULL, 90, 16, 15),
(1406, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/lobsterthermidor_73972\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/lobsterthermidor_73972_16x9.jpg\n', 'Lobster thermidor\n', ' Such a treat on Christmas Eve or for any deluxe special occasion. The chips are gilding the lily, but why not?\n', 30, 90, 2, 14),
(1407, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/vegan_wellington_28288\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/vegan_wellington_28288_16x9.jpg\n', 'Vegan Wellington \n', ' A delicious vegan main course that makes a statement! A row of whole Portobello mushrooms sit alongside pecans, dried cranberries, sweet potatoes and chestnuts in this vegan wellington recipe. \n \n Each serving provides 539 kcal, 9g protein, 48g carbohydrate (of which 10g sugars), 32g fat (of which 5g saturates), 9g fibre and 0.7g salt.\n \n \n', 30, 120, 6, 23),
(1408, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/macaroni_cheese_51582\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/macaroni_cheese_51582_16x9.jpg\n', 'Macaroni cheese with leeks\n', ' This easy four-step recipe for macaroni cheese will please all the family.  Get a little extra vegetables into your mac and cheese with sweet leeks tucked in the cheese sauce and peas alongside.\n', 30, 90, 4, 12),
(1409, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/macaroons_04669\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/macaroons_04669_16x9.jpg\n', 'Macaroons\n', ' Beautiful macaroons are one of the current ‘sweet’ crazes. Make a batch, put them in a pretty box tied up with ribbon, and give them to a friend as a dazzling gift.\n \n Equipment and preparation: You will need a piping bag fitted with a 1cm/½in nozzle.\n', 90, 30, 24, 9),
(1410, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/oven_chips_67210\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p07r2vq4.jpg\n', 'Oven chips\n', ' Eating healthily doesn’t mean you have to cut out your favourite dishes. By cooking these chips in the oven you dramatically reduce the amount of oil used. \n', 30, 30, 1, 4),
(1411, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pancakes_with_berries_54226\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/pancakes_with_berries_54226_16x9.jpg\n', 'Pancakes with berries and white chocolate\n', ' This seriously easy and traditional pancake recipe is even fit for a dinner party dessert thanks to the toppings.\n', 30, 30, 4, 7),
(1412, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/classiccottagepie_90765\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/classiccottagepie_90765_16x9.jpg\n', 'Easy cottage pie\n', ' James Martin \'s easy cottage pie recipe is a family favourite on a weeknight. He goes back to basics to show you how to make a classic version, but easier.\n', 30, 120, 4, 18),
(1413, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/whole_sea_bass_with_38333\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/whole_sea_bass_with_38333_16x9.jpg\n', 'Whole sea bass with warmed tomato and citrus salsa\n', ' Cooking a whole fish looks so impressive and the warmed salsa has a lovely zingy citrus flavour.\n', 30, 30, 4, 16),
(1414, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mincedbeefpie_89198\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mincedbeefpie_89198_16x9.jpg\n', 'Minced beef pie\n', ' This tasty and easy beef pie recipe will quickly become a family favourite. Serve with mounds of mash.\n', 30, 90, 4, 10),
(1415, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/anything-goes_frittata_95480\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/anything-goes_frittata_95480_16x9.jpg\n', 'Anything-goes frittata\n', ' This frittata recipe is super flexible. You can use just about anything that\'s leftover in the fridge.  \n \n Each serving provides 337 kcal, 21g protein, 15g carbohydrates (of which 5g sugars), 21g fat (of which 7g saturates), 4.5g fibre and 1g salt.\n', 30, 30, 4, 15),
(1416, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/cranachan_49732\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/cranachan_49732_16x9.jpg\n', 'Cranachan\n', ' It\'s super easy to whip up Mary Berry\'s classic Scottish cranachan. Hold back some of the crunchy oats and raspberries for a pretty topping, but don\'t hold back on the whisky!\n', 30, 10, 8, 7),
(1417, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/pork_with_a_creamy_59984\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/pork_with_a_creamy_59984_16x9.jpg\n', 'Pork with a creamy mushroom sauce\n', ' Lean pork contains around 4% fat, so is a good choice if you’re on a diet. The pork medallion is quick to cook and makes a good alternative to chicken.\n \n Each serving provides 315 kcal, 29g protein, 8.5g carbohydrate (of which 7g sugars), 18g fat (of which 7g saturates), 3.5g fibre and 0.3g salt.\n \n \n', 30, 30, 1, 12),
(1418, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/orange_butterfly_cakes_82059\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/orange_butterfly_cakes_82059_16x9.jpg\n', 'Orange butterfly cakes \n', ' Mary Berry\'s easy butterfly fairy cakes are filled with orange curd and topped with icing. \n \n Equipment and preparation: you will need a bun tin lined with 12 fairy cake cases.\n \n \n', 30, 30, 12, 10),
(1419, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/finnish_pancakes_26537\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/finnish_pancakes_26537_16x9.jpg\n', 'Finnish pancakes\n', ' A cross between a Yorkshire pudding and a pancake, served with a sweet topping of your choice – what’s not to like? \n', 90, 30, 6, 11),
(1420, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/moroccanlambtaginewi_84062\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/moroccanlambtaginewi_84062_16x9.jpg\n', 'Moroccan lamb tagine with lemon and pomegranate couscous\n', ' This aromatic lamb tagine can be made in advance and reheated. Make the fruity lemon couscous just before serving.\n', 30, 120, 12, 29),
(1421, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/oriental_vegetable_99308\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/oriental_vegetable_99308_16x9.jpg\n', 'Vietnamese-style crayfish and noodle salad\n', ' I adore this light and fresh crayfish salad. Buy the freshest, finest ingredients you can – this dish is all about fresh flavours. \n', 30, 10, 6, 23),
(1422, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/star_mincemeat_and_22337\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/star_mincemeat_and_22337_16x9.jpg\n', 'Mincemeat and marzipan tart\n', ' Mary Berry shows you the easiest way to make mince pies en masse! A hidden layer of marzipan is a lovely surprise, but to make it even easier add the mincemeat in one layer with the grated marzipan and pastry stars on top. \n \n For this recipe you will need a 5cm/2in star cutter and a 36x12cm/14x4½in loose-bottomed tranche tin (alternatively use a 23cm/9in loose-bottomed round tart tin).\n \n \n', 90, 90, 8, 8),
(1423, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/carrot_cake_muffins_57211\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/carrot_cake_muffins_57211_16x9.jpg\n', 'Carrot cake muffins\n', ' Mary Berry ensures you can have all the same flavours of carrot cake in a respectable muffin, plus the sweet cream cheese icing as a surprise filling.\n', 30, 30, 12, 13),
(1424, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/egg_bacon_and_asparagus_32159\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/egg_bacon_and_asparagus_32159_16x9.jpg\n', 'Egg, bacon and asparagus flan\n', ' A light tart that melts in the mouth, this feels like a real treat and it’s a cinch to make. There’s not even any rolling involved. If you like, leave asparagus out of the filling mixture or add extra ingredients of your own. Sautéed mushrooms, blanched broccoli and roasted peppers all work well. 245 calories per portion\n', 90, 90, 6, 12),
(1425, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/barnsley_chops_with_60141\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/barnsley_chops_with_60141_16x9.jpg\n', 'Barnsley chops with Cumberland sauce\n', ' A double-sided chop deserves pride of place at the dinner table, so serve this tender and juicy lamb recipe with a classic Cumberland sauce.\n', 30, 30, 4, 13),
(1426, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/quickhummousandolive_71473\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/quickhummousandolive_71473_16x9.jpg\n', 'Quick hummus\n', ' This easy hummus recipe is great to make sandwiches for your lunchbox, or simply to serve with breadsticks or pitta.\n \n Each serving provides 378 kcal, 13.5g protein, 47g carbohydrates (of which 1.5g sugars), 13.5g fat (of which 2g saturates), 7g fibre and 0.9g salt.\n', 30, 10, 3, 11),
(1427, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/ham_and_cheese_crown_40328\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/ham_and_cheese_crown_40328_16x9.jpg\n', 'Ham and cheese crown \n', ' One crown, many kings. Pastry, ham and gouda cheese combine to make a breakfast fit for kings in this wonderful centrepiece.\n', 30, 30, 10, 9),
(1428, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/smashed_avocado_on_toast_89082\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/smashed_avocado_on_toast_89082_16x9.jpg\n', 'Smashed avocado on toast\n', ' So simple and delicious, this is perfect when you need a quick and nutritious breakfast or snack. \n', 30, NULL, 1, 9),
(1429, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/roastbeetroot_72797\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/roastbeetroot_72797_16x9.jpg\n', 'Roast beetroot\n', ' A really simple and delicious way to cook beetroot. The sweet and mellow flavours complement roast chicken perfectly.\n', 30, 120, 4, 10),
(1430, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/15_minute_pasta_33407\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/15_minute_pasta_33407_16x9.jpg\n', '15 minute pasta\n', ' This is my standby pasta supper as it is so delicious, so quick and everyone loves it. Great for everyday or for casual supper parties too.\n', 30, 30, 6, 11),
(1431, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/slow_cooker_pork_74189\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/slow_cooker_pork_74189_16x9.jpg\n', 'Slow cooker pork shoulder with butterbeans, apple and sage\n', ' Crispy fried sage adds a special touch to this easy slow-cooker pork recipe.\n', 30, 120, 4, 15),
(1432, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/harissa_polenta_with_98148\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/harissa_polenta_with_98148_16x9.jpg\n', 'Harissa polenta with sautéed vegetables\n', ' A simple vegan and gluten-free dinner that’s ready in 20 minutes. Use whatever greens you have in the fridge to top this spicy, fragrant polenta. \n \n Each serving provides 594 kcal, 12g protein, 67g carbohydrates (of which 4g sugars), 29g fat (of which 3g saturates), 7.5g fibre and 1.6g salt.\n', 30, 30, 2, 11),
(1433, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/scotchbroth_8116\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/scotchbroth_8116_16x9.jpg\n', 'Scotch broth\n', ' This cheap and cheerful soup is perfect for the slow cooker  - simply tip in all the ingredients and cook on high for 6-8 hours (or until the barley is soft).\n', 120, 120, 6, 14),
(1434, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/christmascake_2359\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/christmascake_2359_16x9.jpg\n', 'Christmas cake\n', ' This traditional Christmas cake pulls out all the stops - if you have the time, feed it with brandy in the run up to Christmas.\n', 90, 120, 8, 21),
(1435, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/lamb_steak_with_minty_38336\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/lamb_steak_with_minty_38336_16x9.jpg\n', 'Lamb steak with minty broad beans\n', ' Fancy changing up your barbecue offering? It doesn\'t get much better than lamb on a bed of herby broad beans.\n', 30, 30, 4, 19),
(1436, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/mutton_chops_with_potato_75289\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/mutton_chops_with_potato_75289_16x9.jpg\n', 'Mutton chops with potato and turnip gratin \n', ' Mutton, potatoes and turnips are given a bit of flair with sauce gribiche and lashings of cream.\n', 30, 90, 6, 29),
(1437, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/griddledhalloumi_79154\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/griddledhalloumi_79154_16x9.jpg\n', 'Griddled halloumi\n', ' Grilled halloumi and marinated courgette ribbons make an easy open sandwich for parties or supper for one.\n', 30, 30, 1, 7),
(1438, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/traditional_honey-glazed_52289\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/traditional_honey-glazed_52289_16x9.jpg\n', 'Honey-glazed gammon\n', ' Of all our gammon recipes, this is a festive classic. The Hairy Bikers know this is a must-have for a Christmas party!\n \n Each serving provides 327 kcal, 36g protein, 10g carbohydrates (of which 10g sugars), 15.5g fat (of which 5g saturates), 1.5g fibre and 4.9g salt.\n', 30, 120, 10, 9),
(1439, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/quesadilla_84511\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/quesadilla_84511_16x9.jpg\n', 'Easy vegetarian quesadilla\n', ' Super easy, cheap and quick to make, quesadillas are what you need when you\'re so hungry you could eat your own face. You\'ve probably got all the ingredients for these veggie quesadillas in your cupboard and fridge right now. \n \n Each serving provides 882 kcal, 36g protein, 88g carbohydrates (of which 8g sugars), 40.5g fat (of which 19g saturates), 11g fibre and 2.8g salt.\n', 30, 30, 2, 9),
(1440, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/cider_and_5-spice_bundt_05085\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/cider_and_5-spice_bundt_05085_16x9.jpg\n', 'Cider and five-spice bundt cake\n', ' Most of the time I refer to this as my Cider and five-spice gingerbread, but I changed the name out of concern for those who expect a little more gingeriness from their gingerbead. If you want to intensify the ginger element, use 250ml/9fl oz ginger beer in place of the cider.\n \n This cake is wonderful enough plain as it is, though I have something of a faiblesse for the gleaming accompaniment of the smoky salted caramel sauce, as you can see from the picture.\n \n \n \n For this recipe you will need a 2½/4½ pints litre capacity bundt tin or a 20cm/8in square cake tin (approx. 5½cm/2¼in deep).\n', 30, 90, 1, 21);
INSERT INTO `recipe_info` (`recipe_id`, `recipe_url`, `image_url`, `title`, `description`, `preparation_time`, `cook_time`, `serving_count`, `ingredient_count`) VALUES
(1441, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/steamedseabassinhotb_89271\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/steamedseabassinhotb_89271_16x9.jpg\n', 'Steamed sea bass in hot beer and ginger lime sauce\n', ' This simple and elegant sea bass recipe makes the most of this delicious fish.\n', 30, 30, 2, 18),
(1442, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/stuffedportabellamus_85840\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/stuffedportabellamus_85840_16x9.jpg\n', 'Stuffed Portobello mushrooms with blue cheese \n', ' An easy starter for dinner parties or a simple meal for one served with some fresh crusty bread to mop up the juices.\n', 30, 30, 1, 13),
(1443, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/red_pepper_and_aubergine_84745\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/red_pepper_and_aubergine_84745_16x9.jpg\n', 'Shakshuka traybake\n', ' Perfect for a lazy weekend, this shakshuka traybake recipe allows you to slowly roast vegetables in the oven while you have a snooze. \n \n Each serving provides 237 kcal, 11g protein, 16.5g carbohydrates (of which 16g sugars), 12g fat (of which 2.5g saturates), 8.5g fibre and 0.3g salt. \n', 30, 90, 4, 15),
(1444, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/slow_cooker_beef_curry_13533\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/slow_cooker_beef_curry_13533_16x9.jpg\n', 'Slow cooker beef curry\n', ' Use your slow cooker for this simple beef curry - it’s full of flavour and guarantees meltingly tender beef. Serve with rice and naan bread.\n \n Each serving provides 334 kcal, 33g protein, 12g carbohydrates (of which 10g sugars), 16.5g fat (of which 5g saturates), 2g fibre and 0.3g salt.\n', 30, 120, 6, 14),
(1445, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/deep-filled_homity_pie_48616\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/deep-filled_homity_pie_48616_16x9.jpg\n', 'Deep-filled homity pie\n', ' Rich wholemeal pastry packed with a potato, onion and cheese filling. We’ve added spinach and a hint of nutmeg for a Biker twist. \n', 30, 90, 6, 18),
(1446, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/chickencurry_82610\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/chickencurry_82610_16x9.jpg\n', 'Chicken curry for one\n', ' This tasty chicken curry is perfect for solo cooking on a budget. It\'s also ready in no time, faster than a trip to the takeaway!\n', 30, 30, 1, 7),
(1447, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/appleandpassionfruit_89981\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/appleandpassionfruit_89981_16x9.jpg\n', 'Apple and passion fruit tartlets\n', ' These crisp, custardy tartlets with fragrant sharp passion fruit are sure to win any girl\'s heart. They make a good breakfast, too!\n', 120, 30, 6, 14),
(1448, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/victoria_sponge_with_18011\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/832xn/p03cvv0d.jpg\n', 'Victoria sponge with mixed berries\n', ' This fancy Victoria sponge is filled with fresh cream and syrup-coated berries for a special teatime treat.\n', 30, 90, 6, 12),
(1449, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/croquemonsieur_90049\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/croquemonsieur_90049_16x9.jpg\n', 'Croque monsieur\n', ' If you could only make one dish, it arguably should be this amazingly gooey croque monsieur (that\'s a toasted ham and cheese sandwich). Hersha Patel shows you how to make the easiest white sauce that will elevate the ham and cheese toastie to new heights.\n', 30, 10, 2, 11),
(1450, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/lemon_pavlova_50340\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/lemon_pavlova_50340_16x9.jpg\n', 'Lemon pavlova\n', ' Ever since my first pav in \'How To Eat\', I have been something of a pavaholic. For me, acidity is key. I never understood why anyone would pile sweet fruit on top of something that is essentially – and dreamily – a cross between a marshmallow and a meringue. I had the idea – yes, really – from the actor Michael Sheen. I saw him create a  great pile of lemony pavs on The Great Comic Relief Bake Off, and it inspired me. Diolch Michael (if I may).\n', 30, 120, 8, 7),
(1451, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/bolognaise_ragu_with_66037\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/bolognaise_ragu_with_66037_16x9.jpg\n', 'Bolognese ragù with pappardelle \n', ' Bolognese is such a classic everyday dish loved by young and old and Mary\'s slow-cooked sauce won\'t disappoint. \n', 30, 120, 6, 20),
(1452, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/beef_and_mushroom_99051\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/beef_and_mushroom_99051_16x9.jpg\n', 'Healthy beef and mushroom stroganoff\n', ' A comforting, healthy and creamy dish that’s ready in a flash. This light version of beef stroganoff is a little over 500 calories so it is recommended you pair it with a lower calorie breakfast or lunch on a diet day to ensure your calorie intake doesn\'t exceed 1200–1500.\n \n Each serving provides 546 kcal, 41g protein, 64g carbohydrates (of which 9g sugars), 14g fat (of which 3.5g saturates), 8g fibre and 1g salt. \n', 30, 30, 2, 16),
(1453, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/broad_bean_mange_tout_00471\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/broad_bean_mange_tout_00471_16x9.jpg\n', 'Warm salad of broad beans, peas, beetroot and mozzarella\n', ' Sweet roast beetroot and shallots mixed with seasonal veg warmed in a sharp sour-sweet dressing. Add mozzarella and a final blue cheese dressing for heaven on a plate.\n', 30, 90, 4, 21),
(1454, 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/easy_vegetarian_tacos_88736\n', 'https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_832/recipes/easy_vegetarian_tacos_88736_16x9.jpg\n', 'Easy vegetarian tacos\n', ' Vegetarian tacos are fun and easy to make. Everyone can help themselves to the crunchy corn tacos, spicy bean filling, creamy avocado, soured cream and grated cheese.\n \n If you\'re making this recipe with children, see the tips section for advice on kitchen safety.  \n', 30, 30, 4, 14),
